    description:
      '\u003ch2\u003e\r\n    Job description\r\n\u003c/h2\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003ca id="toggle-1" href="https://www.accenture.com/fi-en/careers/jobdetails?id=00348580_en#0-collapsible"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv id="0-collapsible"\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                Accenture Technology Summer Internship\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                If you join Accenture you can make great ideas happen for some of the world\'s most dynamic companies. With broad global resources and deep\r\n                technical know-how, we collaborate with clients to cultivate ideas and deliver results. Choose a career at Accenture and enjoy an innovative\r\n                environment where challenging and interesting work is part of daily life.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                We are looking for enthusiastic IT students for \u003cstrong\u003esummer internship \u003c/strong\u003efor Accenture Technology. Internship period lasts from June\r\n                to August 2016. Trainee positions are located in the Helsinki metropolitan area.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                You will be working in an innovative environment with access to the global resources and expertise. Throughout your internship you\'ll work on a\r\n                real project role. Rather than just shadowing someone, you will be a fully-fledged member of the team right from the start, with\r\n                responsibilities that could involve, depending on your background and interests; requirement definition, programming, testing software,\r\n                conducting research, writing reports or analyzing data.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                We offer a competitive salary and benefits such as health care, extensive training and flexible work arrangements, wellbeing activities,\r\n                Accenture FUN club, etc. We will connect you with a "buddy" who will be there to offer help and advice whenever you need it. Many of our\r\n                previous summer interns have become permanent Accenture employees after they graduate.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003ch2\u003e\r\n    Basic qualifications\r\n\u003c/h2\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003ca id="toggle-1" href="https://www.accenture.com/fi-en/careers/jobdetails?id=00348580_en#1-collapsible"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv id="1-collapsible"\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                \u003cstrong\u003eQualifications\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cul\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    You are a technology student from University or University of Applied Sciences, preferably within one of the following areas:\r\n                    \u003cul\u003e\r\n                        \u003cli\u003e\r\n                            Engineering (all disciplines)\r\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                        \u003cli\u003e\r\n                            Computer Science / Computer Engineering\r\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                        \u003cli\u003e\r\n                            Information Systems\r\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                        \u003cli\u003e\r\n                            Mathematics / Statistics / Sciences\r\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    You have strong academic results from high school and university\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    You have desire to work with IT in a project oriented environment\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    You are team-oriented and have an outgoing personality\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    You have excellent communication skills (written and oral) in both Finnish and English. Please note that excellent Finnish is a mandatory\r\n                    requirement.\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                Does this sound like the perfect start for your professional career? Make your move - apply online latest 30.01.2016! Please note we process\r\n                applications as they come and start interviews already during the application period.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                In your application please attach your CV and a cover letter with salary request in English and electronic copies of your excerpt from the\r\n                student registry and upper secondary school matriculation certificate. We look forward to receiving your application!\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                Accenture welcomes and encourages applications from diverse backgrounds related to gender, age, ethnicity, culture, race, religion and belief,\r\n                disability, nationality, sexual orientation and gender identity. Inclusion and diversity are fundamental to our culture and core values,\r\n                providing an environment where everyone brings distinct experience, talent and culture to their work. We invite you to be part of this\r\n                diversity!\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                Please note: applications without CV, grade transcripts and application will not be evaluated. Please ensure that these documents are attached\r\n                before completing the application.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n',
