    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Are you an outstanding student with a can-do attitude? Do you want to join us on the exciting transformation journey that we have embarked on? Then you\r\n    might be our future graduate.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Nordea Graduate programme kick-starts your transition from being a student to becoming a successful young professional, creating the perfect start for your\r\n    career. You will be employed in a specific position matching your interests and competencies and giving you an opportunity to work in a field that you are\r\n    passionate about.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Recruitment is ongoing until \u003cstrong\u003e14\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003csup\u003eth\u003c/sup\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e February\u003c/strong\u003e.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eVacant positions include:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.nordea.com/en/career/vacant-positions/jobdetails.html?jobid=197212-Graduate-to-Retail-Banking-IT-and-Digital-Banking\u0026amp;blq=cty=19420%257Cgeo=0%257Carea=19483"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Graduate to Retail Banking IT and Digital Banking\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.nordea.com/en/career/vacant-positions/jobdetails.html?jobid=197210-Graduate-to-Nordea-Trade-Finance-Systems\u0026amp;blq=cty=19420%257Cgeo=0%257Carea=19483"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Graduate to Nordea Trade Finance Systems\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.nordea.com/en/career/vacant-positions/jobdetails.html?jobid=197211-Graduate-to-Payment-Platform-Foundation-Development\u0026amp;blq=cty=19420%257Cgeo=0%257Carea=19483"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Graduate to Payment Platform Foundation Development\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nAll the available graduate positions can be found    \u003ca href="http://www.nordea.com/fi/ura/avoimet-tehtavat/index.html?cty=0\u0026amp;geo=0\u0026amp;area=19483\u0026amp;jobid="\u003ehere.\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The minimum requirement as a graduate at Nordea is that you have a Master’s degree, a maximum of two years’ post-academic work experience, excellent\r\n    English language skills and high potential. Specific recruitment criteria are defined in each job ad.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Furthermore, in the recruitment process you need to pass an ability test, where your numerical, verbal and inductive capabilities are tested.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eFind out more from here:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="http://www.nordea.com/en/career/nordea-graduate-programme/index.html"\u003eNordea Graduate programme\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="http://nordeagraduatehaku.fi/"\u003eNordea Graduate -haku\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Facebook: \u003ca href="https://www.facebook.com/Nordea-Graduate-haku-702272789856760/"\u003eNordea Graduate -haku\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n',
