    description:
      "\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Have you dreamed of taking part in something small, progressive and\r\n    interesting from the\r\n    very early stage? Have you looked for ideas and innovations, things that\r\n    could be changed\r\n    or made more engaging, simply using the development skills you possess?\r\n    Look no more –\r\n    we have the idea, a ready-made foundation and a position open for someone\r\n    with an\r\n    adventurous mindset, curious of the entrepreneurial landscape!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Our small but feisty lineup is now looking for additional competence to the\r\n    technical corner of\r\n    our team. We are currently at the pre-testing phase, where we are tweaking\r\n    and finalizing\r\n    the tech for a beta version of the product. After we receive insight from\r\n    our test users, we will\r\n    enter the fundraising stage.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    The core of the idea is to change the way we listen to music, make it more\r\n    social and help\r\n    our users find new beats. We want to enable people to dive beyond the worn\r\n    out songs we\r\n    hear every day, pair users with similar music taste and find out what folks\r\n    around you are\r\n    listening to. We all know that feeling when a song that you’ve never heard\r\n    before hits your\r\n    ears and explodes into instant love! That’s pretty much the essence of what\r\n    we want to do!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    The position, or rather the spot in our team, can be handled alongside\r\n    studies or a job for the\r\n    time being. We are looking for someone who shares our passion for changing\r\n    the music\r\n    landscape, is a cool guy or a lady and doesn’t take life too seriously. We\r\n    would love if you\r\n    have some experience working on the front-end (iOS), but the current focus\r\n    is more on the\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    backend stack:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Linux (Ubuntu 18.04 LTS)\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Docker\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Python (3.7)\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - PostgreSQL\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Django\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    The new teammate will be offered a share of our up and running company.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    If this sounds like something you are looking for, throw us an e-mail to\r\n    kalle@mudarmusic.com or call +358503845100. We don’t need anything formal,\r\n    just tell us\r\n    a little about yourself, and what kind of technologies you have experience\r\n    with. The rest we\r\n    can take over a beer, a cup of coffee or tea!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Best regards,\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    The Mudar team\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Kalle, Fredi, Dan, Niko\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
