    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is looking for an exceptional software engineer who has the passion for solving challenging tasks in cutting-edge networking technologies.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is the fifth fastest growing software company in Europe, its software is shipped in 3 mobiles, tablets, cars or other devices every second.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The candidate will participate in the design and implementation of robust and high-performance products utilized by top brands around the globe. Candidate\r\n    should possess genuine enthusiasm for results and a will to achieve them both independently and as a team member.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Responsibilities:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Design and development of software products utilizing the latest networking technologies.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Analyzing performance bottlenecks, finding and implementing improvements.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Debugging interoperability and reliability issues.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Providing technical support for new and existing products.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Writing documentation for the new products and solutions.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Testing and verification of the new products and solutions.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Working together with team members following Agile methodologies.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Required Experience:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Expert in C/C++.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in developing for embedded and resource constrained platforms.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Deep understanding of network protocols especially device discovery and NAT traversal protocols.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Very good understanding of transport layer protocols such as TCP and UDP.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in working with UPnP, WebSockets, RTP and SOAP.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Preferred Experience:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiarity with DLNA, DIAL, RTP, RTSP, XML.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiarity with media streaming protocols such as HLS, MPEG-DASH, HDS and Smooth Streaming protocol.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in multicast protocols and multicast based DNS service.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Writing portable software, knowledge of several operating systems\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiarity with Network security and DRM techniques.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        BSc or MSc in Computer Science or equivalent skills\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Benefits:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Dynamic work environment, with flexible working hours.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Laptop, smartphone, health insurance, lunch coupons, and more.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    How to apply:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    This position is full-time. Tuxera headquarters are located in Ruoholahti, Helsinki, Finland. The position will be filled once a suitable candidate is\r\n    found. Please apply at the \u003ca target="_blank" href="http://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/job-application/?aguid=4E166F91E38448388AFC3A270D394B6A"\u003eTuxera website\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
