    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Now we are looking for a talented, proactive and quality-oriented Mobile\r\n    Application Developer to join Ecolane’s constantly growing team. In this\r\n    role, your main responsibility will be developing Ecolane’s mobile\r\n    application for the end users of the transportation service. You will be\r\n    working side by side with an experienced mobile application developer\r\n    creating new features as well as fixing bugs. The position will be modified\r\n    to your skill set and interests, so you could be a future mobile\r\n    application expert starting your career or an already highly skilled\r\n    professional. Ecolane guarantees that you will be learning a lot of new\r\n    things in your role, and you will have the possibility to expand to other\r\n    development areas in the team based on your skills and interests.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    You will be joining a team of talented and enthusiastic people, where each\r\n    person takes both pride in and responsibility for making Ecolane’s product\r\n    even better. You should be willing to solve problems independently but have\r\n    no fear of communicating with others or questioning the existing solutions.\r\n    Ecolane’s management and processes will make sure that you have the support\r\n    you need for your work and a working environment that supports a healthy\r\n    work-life balance.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat Ecolane is looking for:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        An understanding of mobile application development\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in native Android or iOS development through work or hobby\r\n        (Swift, Kotlin, or Java)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Basic skills in C# and Visual Studio or hybrid mobile application\r\n        development\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in REST calls\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Fluent English skills\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat Ecolane sees as an advantage:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        One or more native applications published on Google Play Store or Apple\r\n        App Store\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of Amazon Alexa, Android Auto, or wearables development\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Basic skills in server-side development\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat Ecolane can offer:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        An opportunity to be part of responsible and meaningful product\r\n        development\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        An independent role and the possibility to influence the way you work\r\n        and solve problems\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A great opportunity to develop as a software professional\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Flexible working hours and a cozy office\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Great work benefits (lunch, phone, healthcare, insurance, gym etc.)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        An opportunity to gain deep insight into and knowledge of a changing\r\n        industry\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A relaxed working atmosphere and super nice colleagues: Ecolane’s\r\n        people look after each other\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    If you’re the Mobile App Developer we’re looking for, send your CV and\r\n    application in PDF format latest on 11.11.2018 here:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://apply.atalent.fi/ecolane-mobile-app-developer-10-2018"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://apply.atalent.fi/ecolane-mobile-app-developer-10-2018\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    . Tell us what you have done with the required technologies and what kind\r\n    of projects you have worked on before. Please mention your earliest\r\n    possible starting date and salary request.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
