    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Euformatics is looking for a Software Developer to work on their innovative\r\n    bioinformatics tools. In this position, you would join Euformatics’ product\r\n    development team of three that focuses on developing their solutions\r\n    further. You would start first working on a smaller entity and once you get\r\n    familiar with their software take on more responsibility. In the beginning,\r\n    you could be working for example with user interface development or\r\n    database integration.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Euformatics is looking for someone who shares their passion for healthtech\r\n    and is genuinely interested in genomics. You don’t have to be an expert in\r\n    the field yet but you should have an open-minded attitude to learn more as\r\n    Euformatics’ team is ready to teach you and give you support. It will\r\n    require courage from you to ask for help when you need it and patience to\r\n    accept that you won’t understand everything right away. Euformatics has new\r\n    projects coming up which is why they are hoping that you would be able to\r\n    start as soon as possible.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eEuformatics is looking for someone with:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        skills in HTML, CSS, JavaScript and SQL\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        basic knowledge in biology\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        good spoken and written communication skills in English\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eEuformatics considers as an asset:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        skills in Java, Python, Linux or Cloud technologies\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        previous work experience in programming\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Finnish language skills\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eEuformatics and this position offer you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        a chance to work on solutions that really have an impact on human\r\n        lives. Euformatics’ solutions are used for example for curing cancer or\r\n        identifying growth disorders\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        an opportunity to grow into a strong bio-it professional with the\r\n        support of an experienced team\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        flexibility – once you get the hang of things you can work remotely and\r\n        during the time of day that suits you best, the most important thing is\r\n        to get your tasks done\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        working environment with a low hierarchy\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        a chance to see and experience the shifting landscape of the health\r\n        sector\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Got excited? Please submit your CV and application letter in PDF by latest\r\n    on November 7th 2018 here:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://apply.atalent.fi/euformatics-software-developer-10-2018"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://apply.atalent.fi/euformatics-software-developer-10-2018\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    . Note that we go through the applications already during the application\r\n    period. If you have a GitHub profile or equivalent, we would be happy to\r\n    have a look at it as well.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
