    tags: [],
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is looking for summer trainees who have a passion for solving\r\n    challenging problems in cutting-edge data storage solutions and\r\n    interoperability software. As a summer trainee, you get more than this\r\n    summer experience - you will interact on a daily basis with professionals\r\n    from the most successful worldwide brands who trust in Tuxera file systems\r\n    and services.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your mission is to ensure that the software delivered to Tuxera\'s customers\r\n    have passed rigorous quality assurance, customized to any possible hardware\r\n    and software environment.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch3\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eThe team\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The position is part of our Tuxera Quality Assurance team. You will be\r\n    working as part of an extremely skilled and innovative team of Engineers,\r\n    ready to support your learning every step of the way.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Rostislav (our summer trainee 2016, now Senior Software Engineer) and\r\n    Mikael (our summer trainee 2016, now Software Engineer) also have shared\r\n    their interesting experience in the blogs. Check them out!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="https://www.tuxera.com/blog/not-typical-qa-experience/"\u003e\r\n        “Not your typical QA experience”\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.tuxera.com/blog/professional-aspirations-and-motivational-secrets-at-tuxera/"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        “Professional aspirations and motivational secrets at Tuxera”\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eJunior Software Engineer in Test\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    In this role, you will dive into the Linux kernel and file system\r\n    internals. You will collaborate with software developers and technical\r\n    sales experts, with strong support from your team. You will be working on\r\n    designing and implementing test tooling and integrating existing testing\r\n    tools to a graphical user interface to ensure best-in-class software\r\n    quality.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Design and implement feature and performance tests for our file system\r\n        products\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Design and implement test and automation tooling\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Investigate internal and customer bug reports\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eBackground and Qualifications\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Generally, we prefer\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A genuine passion for software engineering, debugging and solving\r\n        technical issues either on component or system level\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A Linux command line power user, who is skilled in programming with\r\n        scripting languages such as bash and Python\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The following are considered a strong plus\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of Linux system programming in C and tools such as make, gcc,\r\n        etc.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of file systems and operating system internals\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in testing embedded Linux and Android system-level\r\n        development projects\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eReady to jump onboard? Here’s how to apply!\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    This position will be filled as soon as the suitable candidates are found.\r\n    The starting time can be discussed according to business needs and your own\r\n    summer arrangement. To apply, please include your cover letter, CV and\r\n    anything else relevant to showcase your skills.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Please note that the supporting materials or links to showcase your\r\n        professional or hobby project experience will be very helpful.\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch3\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003ch3\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e Benefits\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Great office facilities with free pool and sauna\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Extensive learning opportunities\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Flexible working hours\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Dynamic and international work environment\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Free snacks and drinks throughout the day\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Table tennis and games at the office\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTuxera\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is one of the fastest-growing software companies in Finland. We are\r\n    a global organization and the market leader in data storage solutions and\r\n    interoperability software. Our developers include some of the world’s top\r\n    experts in Linux kernel development, ready to assist our customers with\r\n    embedded Linux system projects.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    With a growing team of 80 professionals from more than 17 nationalities, we\r\n    have been recognized with awards such as the Great Place to Work. Our\r\n    software ships inside 1 billion devices on the market, including\r\n    smartphones, routers, laptops, cars, TVs, drones and many others.Our\r\n    mission: to open the way for people and businesses to reliably store,\r\n    access, and share any type of data on any device.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We envision a future with an infinite number of connected devices. With\r\n    Tuxera at the heart of every device, data is always accessible exactly when\r\n    and where you want it to be.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003ca href="https://tuxera.breezy.hr/p/7f924a8b57cb01-summer-trainee"\u003eApply here!\u003c/a\u003e ',
