    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\nSibesonke is a pioneer among social entreprises that solve global issues with a fresh approach – innovative business models instead of aid. Our mFarming mobile service in Tanzania provides our user base of soon one million farmers with information and contacts to improve farm productivity and profitability. At the same time it brings operational efficiency to our business clients. We serve large corporations and international organizations with customer focus, excellence, and trust.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nSibesonke product development team is based in Otaniemi, Finland.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eJob Description\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nYou will support our team of Ruby / Rails software developers and work on backend and user interface solutions. In our agile team, you will help to bring new product features to birth and see them mature in the market. This will give you a great opportunity to learn from experienced RoR developers and broaden your technology skills. Work time can be flexible while having enough common time with the team in the office to coordinate things.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nMore information about the project can be found here: \u003ca href="http://mfarming.sibesonke.com/"\u003ehttp://mfarming.sibesonke.com/\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we expect from you is\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eProgramming experience in Ruby / Rails. Experience with JavaScript, MySQL, Linux, and Android apps are all a plus. \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eInterest in solving problems in other cultures (Africa)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eSelf-motivation, good listener, good team player\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eEnjoying meaningful work\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nIf this sounds interesting to you we love to receive from you CV, short explanation why you like to work with us and what is your availability. We pay an attractive salary that will depend on your skill level.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nMore information gives our lead developer Timo: \u003ca href="mailto:timo@sibesonke.com"\u003etimo@sibesonke.com\u003c/a\u003e 040-7321482\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
