    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The computational medicine group at Institute of Molecular Medicine Finland (FIMM) is now recruiting a web developer for a database interface design.\r\n    Python, Javascript and SQL are needed. The position can be ideal for a summer student who is willing to start your Master thesis. It can be also extended\r\n    for a PhD position in bioinformatics depending on the performance and funding.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    More details about the group:\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="https://www.fimm.fi/en/research/groups/aittokallio" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n        https://www.fimm.fi/en/research/groups/aittokallio\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nDr. Jing Tang will be the main supervisor so if you are interested please contact Jing Tang (    \u003ca href="mailto:jing.tang@helsinki.fi"\u003ejing.tang@helsinki.fi\u003c/a\u003e) ASAP.\r\n    \r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Best Regards,\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\r\n    Liye He\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
