    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUmbra Summer Experience (Helsinki, Finland)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eWant to learn the ropes from the best?\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eUmbra is on a mission to make it possible to display any 3D content in realtime on any piece of hardware. Umbra\'s solutions are the backbone of a wide range of 3D applications that are used by millions of people every day.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eUmbra is looking for a Junior Programmer who’ll work with us during the summer of 2016, and possibly stay with the team (part-time or full-time) when the autumn comes. Our juniors get to jump in the deep end and work on actual production code - not making coffee or fixing the printer. Assignments include for example programming tools, creating demos and doing cool stuff to impress our jaded engineers.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eTO HAVE A SHOT, THERE ARE TWO MUSTS\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eYou need to have done things already, such as demos or some other projects that you can impress us with.\u003cbr/\u003e\r\nYour cover letter should tell us why you are especially interested in Umbra.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eREQUIRED SKILLS\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eC++ programming\u003cbr/\u003e\r\nSkills or strong interest in 3D graphics programming\u003cbr/\u003e\r\nAny Experience in Unreal Engine, Unity and such would also be great\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eGENERAL REQUIREMENTS TO ALL POSITIONS AT UMBRA\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eBeing able to take initiative and to make things happen\u003cbr/\u003e\r\nSocial personality and and good team player\u003cbr/\u003e\r\nPassion for video games is a plus!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eUmbra offers all kinds of perks, for example challenging tasks, nice compensation, weekly team breakfasts and regular hackathons. Also great parties - you should have been boarded before our 10 year anniversary party...\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eMore information and application form at \u003ca href="http://umbra3d.com/jobs/" target="blank_"\u003ehttp://umbra3d.com/jobs/\u003c/a\u003e. There’s no deadline - we’ll hire the person as soon as we find her/him. Don’t wait too long!\u003c/p\u003e',
