    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href="http://reaktor.com/careers/senior-ios-developer/" target="blank_"\u003ehttp://reaktor.com/careers/senior-ios-developer/\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eReaktor is looking for a Senior iOS Developer to work in our customer project teams. Our clients include such high-profile companies as Supercell, HBO, Finnair, MTV3, Rovio and Michael Kors.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eAs a Senior iOS Developer you’ll be working with a team of experts to build software for all of Apple’s mobile devices, including the iPhone and iPad, tvOS and Apple Watch. We employ cutting-edge technologies such as \u003ca href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxSwift" target="blank_"\u003eRxSwift\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href="https://realm.io/" target="blank_"\u003eRealm\u003c/a\u003e. BaaS platforms are sometimes used to rapidly prototype backend services, and subsequently replaced later with custom software.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eOur standard approach is to put together a team of specialist, each an expert in their own field, working in close relationship with the customer. It is not uncommon for a project to target both iOS and Android platforms. We offer complete freedom to contribute in all the areas you find yourself comfortable with – this means that you are not only allowed, but encouraged to venture into backend development or visual or UX design from time to time.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eWe offer full-time employment with competitive salary and some of the most interesting customers in the Nordic countries and Europe. Our mission is to give you the means and support that you need to unleash your expertise and built something that can transform an entire industry. Fill in your details below or send a quick note to us at \u003ca href="mailto:careers@reaktor.com"\u003ecareers@reaktor.com\u003c/a\u003e! We also have open positions at our \u003ca href="http://reaktor.com/careers/ios-developer/" target="blank_"\u003eNew York\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href="http://reaktor.com/tokyo/" target="blank_"\u003eTokyo \u003c/a\u003eoffices.\u003c/p\u003e',
