    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAt Wunderdog\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    you work in close collaboration with our pack of colleagues and customers\r\n    to build new systems and push existing ones to new levels. While working\r\n    with the customers, for you it is not only about writing top quality code\r\n    but also about continuously improving the development process and the way\r\n    of working the smart way. You enjoy the freedom in your work, e.g.\r\n    selecting the technologies and methods you use, pushing the team to work\r\n    even smarter, and guiding your career based on your interests.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTo be successful in that\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    , we expect you to know your way with modern technologies and methods. It\r\n    doesn’t matter where and how you have gained your skills and experience,\r\n    but that you are hungry to apply them and even more hungry to keep learning\r\n    more.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eThus\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n, we are looking to expand our team with new    \u003cstrong\u003eFullstack Developer\u003c/strong\u003e colleagues.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eOur offering:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Opportunities in learning new skills and acquiring more experience with\r\n        them by working on real customer projects.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        An autonomous work environment where you can apply your skills and\r\n        experience in ways that work best for you.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Possibility to work with an International and dynamic team using the\r\n        tools of your choice.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A culture that nurtures growth and knowledge sharing inside the team.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eOur unreasonable expectations:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Prior experience in working as a \u003cstrong\u003eFullstack Developer\u003c/strong\u003e.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Expertise in modern frontend and backend technologies from previous\r\n        positions.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        High level of knowledge about web applications and web standards.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in using \u003cstrong\u003eDocker\u003c/strong\u003e.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Opinions about the applicability of testing and test usage.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with relational and NoSQL databases.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Basic understanding of \u003cstrong\u003efunctional programming\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        concepts.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Understanding of \u003cstrong\u003eagile\u003c/strong\u003e methodologies.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A high level of self-organization, adaptability, and the ability to\r\n        remain level headed under pressure.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Fluent \u003cstrong\u003eEnglish\u003c/strong\u003e skills, as it is necessary for the\r\n        position.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWho we are:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWunderdog\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    is a software consulting agency established in 2014 in Finland. We are a\r\n    multinational company working with companies ranging in size from start-up\r\n    to enterprise. We help our clients improve their operations by supporting\r\n    the technical development and optimization of their product, service or\r\n    operations. We are a lean organization that has experienced fast growth\r\n    within the last 5 years. In addition to Helsinki, we also operate in\r\n    Germany and Sweden.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Apply to position:\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr" id="docs-internal-guid-1c86a7e8-7fff-b3d6-93b7-abb2f9e0a17e"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://wunderdog.breezy.hr/p/9aa01a0d81cd-fullstack-developer-helsinki-finland/apply"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://wunderdog.breezy.hr/p/9aa01a0d81cd-fullstack-developer-helsinki-finland/apply\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n',
