    description:
      "Kieku Labs Oy is small and agile software development StartUp working on new \r\nways for people to communicate. We are currently located at Aalto Startup Center \r\nin Salmisaari. We offer inspiring work with modern technologies in a fast moving \r\nstartup focused on building a modern audio service for international market. \r\nYou will join a senior team with a wide scope of experience, including lean \r\nproduct development, backend, and data intelligence.\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\nWe are currently looking FullStack developer to build our Web Application. Your \r\njob will include developing frontend and accompanying rest platform. Your team \r\nworking skills and capacity for independent problem solving are important and \r\nhighly valued.\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\nSuccessful applicant has university degree in Computer Science or relevant work \r\nexperience, can work independently and has worked on or learned following \r\ntechnologies:\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n* JavaScript\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n* HTML5\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n* React\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n* Rest\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n* ORM \u0026 SQL\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n* Ruby or interest to learn\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\nIn addition we will appreciate knowledge in any or all of following technologies:\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n* Linux, AWS, DynamoDB, S3, MySQL, Java, Android Development, iOS Development\r\n\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\r\nJob length is 3 month fixed term contract with possibility for extension.\r\n\r\n\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\nFor more info and to apply you can contact:\r\n\r\n\u003cbr /\u003eVeli-Pekka Kestilä \r\n\r\n\u003cbr /\u003evpk@kieku.co / +358503000014",
