    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    The game is on! Supercell is now looking for a Junior Data Scientist for\r\n    the summer to work in their player support team.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        Supercell is a mobile game developer based in the mobile gaming capital\r\n        of the world, Helsinki, with offices in San Francisco, Tokyo, Seoul,\r\n        and Shanghai – all great cities with super talented and super nice\r\n        people. Supercell was founded on three core beliefs: “The Best People\r\n        Make the Best Games”, “Small and independent cells”, and lastly “Games\r\n        that people will play for years”. Thus, our job is to craft games\r\n        played by millions of people all over the world, and since our founding\r\n        in 2010, we have brought five games to the market – Hay Day, Clash of\r\n        Clans, Boom Beach, Clash Royale, and Brawl Stars. To familiarize\r\n        yourself with Supercell, please visit\r\n        \u003ca href="http://supercell.com/en/" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n            http://supercell.com/en/\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n        .\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We are looking for a Junior Data Scientist to work in Supercell’s player\r\n    support team for the summer! In this position, you will help Supercell make\r\n    their games even better for the players by bringing relevant data to the\r\n    table. You will work independently with customer service data which is\r\n    related to e.g. customer satisfaction as well as internal efficiency and\r\n    processes.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWe require:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Relevant educational background, e.g. technical, business, or IT\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Understanding of the basics of data analysis\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Good skills in the following tools: Excel, SQL, and some BI tool (Qlik\r\n        Sense preferred), e.g. from your studies, personal projects, or work\r\n        projects\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Working proficiency in English, both oral and written\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Genuine interest in gaming (experience of specifically Supercell’s\r\n        games is a plus)\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWe see as an advantage:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Proficiency in some statistical programming language, e.g. R or Python\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Previous experience in data analysis or business intelligence\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Previous experience of working in a multicultural environment\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWe offer you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -The opportunity to work in a truly international and skilled team\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Easy-going, enthusiastic, open, and at the same time a very\r\n        results-driven culture\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Great office facilities (including usage of office gym) and location\r\n        in Helsinki\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Flexibility considering working hours and times\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eSkill tags: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        Excel, SQL, BI tool (Qlik Sense preferred)\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eRead more here and apply by 11th April:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003cu\u003e\r\n            \u003ca\r\n                href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/junior-data-scientist-summer-job?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email"\r\n                target="_blank"\r\n            \u003e\r\n                https://atalent.fi/\r\n                \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n                    open-position/junior-data-\r\n                    \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n                        scientist-summer-job?utm_\r\n                        \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n                            source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email\r\n                        \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n                    \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n                \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n            \u003c/a\u003e\r\n        \u003c/u\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
