    description:
      '\u003cdiv title="Page 1"\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                Do you have a passion for mobile back-end/mobile full-stack development and revolutionizing mobile apps? Have you been coding back-end for\r\n                native mobile apps before?\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                OR\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                Do you have a passion for revolutionizing mobile apps that have a great design? Have you been coding and designing native mobile apps before?\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                If you answered YES, you are just the one we are looking for.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                An established startup based in Helsinki is looking for an experienced mobile back- end/mobile full-stack developer that has a particular\r\n                interest for mobile apps and is experienced with Amazon Web Service BaaS tools and servers (AWS). We are also looking for an experienced mobile\r\n                app/mobile front-end developer.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                An ideal candidate is an experienced mobile back-end or mobile full-stack developer with good knowledge of AWS, has built back-end for native\r\n                iOS or Android apps before, is otherwise a skilled programmer, has good knowledge of JavaScript and Python and is passionate about mobile apps.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                OR\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                An ideal candidate is experienced mobile app/mobile front-end developer who has programmed native iOS and Android apps before, is otherwise a\r\n                skilled programmer, has good knowledge of Objective-C, Swift and Java and is passionate about mobile apps. If you have an eye for great app\r\n                design and UX, that’s a big plus!\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                What we seek:\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cul\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        A person with a can-do-attitude and desire to join a startup team\r\n                                   \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Person who is motivated, organized and takes responsibility\r\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    \r\n                        Person who is able to work independently\r\n                    \r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                \r\n                        A developer who wants to code something really cool and at the same time make a\r\n                                        difference\r\n               \r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                                       Hardworking, humble and down to earth person with high integrity\r\n                               \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n               \r\n                        Takes job seriously but with the right amount of humor\r\n                               \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n               \r\n                        Passion for back-end development for native mobile apps\r\n               \r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n               \r\n                        Experienced mobile back-end or mobile full-stack developer who have developed\r\n                        back-end for mobile apps using AWS-tools for both iOS and Android\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Experienced mobile back-end or mobile full-stack developer who has experience in\r\n                        JavaScript and Python OR\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Passion for mobile app and mobile front-end development\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Experienced mobile app/mobile front-end developer who has developed native\r\n                        mobile apps for both iOS and Android\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Experienced mobile app/mobile front-end developer who has good knowledge of\r\n                        Objective C, Swift and Java What we offer:\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv title="Page 2"\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cp\u003e\r\n                Mobile back-end/mobile full-stack developer OR Mobile app/mobile front-end developer\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n            \u003cul\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n               \r\n         Motivating and cool job in a startup\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Virtual office, you can basically work from anywhere in the world i.e. you are not\r\n                        required to be at the office all the time\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Chance to be part of building the most influential consumer mobile apps\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Chance to become one of the core team members and be part of building a new\r\n                        growth company\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Excellent career possibilities and awesome co-workers\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\r\n                    \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Chance to make a difference\r\n                    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n                    \u003cp\u003e\r\n                        Brief description:\r\n                    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n                    \u003cp\u003e\r\n                        As a mobile back-end/mobile full-stack developer, your responsibility is to code together with the team a super solid back-end\r\n                        infrastructure (built on AWS BaaS tools and servers) for revolutionizing consumer mobile apps\r\n                    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n                    \u003cp\u003e\r\n                        As a mobile app/mobile front-end developer, your responsibility is to code and develop together with the team mobile apps, with great\r\n                        UX, ultra minimalistic design and UI for revolutionizing consumer mobile apps\r\n                    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n                    \u003cp\u003e\r\n                        If you got interested send us your CV and short letter of application (one-pager) in PDF format. Please also include links to your\r\n                        LinkedIn and GitHub profiles.\r\n                    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n                    \u003cp\u003e\r\n                        First app is already in the making and we are currently in stealth mode. Position will be filled directly when the right candidate is\r\n                        found.\r\n                    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n                    \u003cp\u003e\r\n                        Marc-Johann Seppänen\r\n                        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n                        CEO \u0026amp; Founder\r\n                        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n                        Guardian Technologies Oy\r\n                        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n                        040 718 3939/marcjohann.m@gmail.com\r\n                    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
