      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Were looking for a super enthusiastic and talented Junior Web Developer who wants to lead a strong role in our passionate and talented team.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    As Junior Web Developer you would be in working on our web application working with a fresh and exciting technology stack. We’re a very lean company and\r\n    you have your say in things varying from UI and UX design to using new and exciting technologies.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Our technology stack includes Ruby on Rails, React, ES6, jQuery, PostgreSQL.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • A chance to work on meaningful but challenging solutions with an extremely motivated and fun team\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Equity in the company\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Kick-ass Apple devices\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • A fresh office in the center of Helsinki with fun and friendly colleagues\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • A chance to work both in Helsinki and San Francisco\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Pizza\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe hope you have most of these:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • At least 1 year experience working with Ruby on Rails applications (preferably other projects than just school obligatory work)\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Basic web development skills (HTML/CSS/git)\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • A great personality and “can do”-attitude\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Passion for sports\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eNice if you have:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Experience with ES6 and or React\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Experience with deploying Rails applications to production\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Experience with AWS, Continuous Integration\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAbout Amper\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Amper is making it easier to play more sports by creating innovative software solutions. Our talented and ambitious core team is backed by some of the best\r\n    people in business and sports. Amper is founded by two Finnish entrepreneurs with the mind set of conquering the world by developing kick-ass products\r\n    while having fun.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Amper Sports Inc. is a US startup with presence both in Helsinki and California.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\nSend your resume and application to \u003ca href="mailto:jobs@ampersports.com"\u003ejobs@ampersports.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
