    description:
      '\u003ch3\u003e\r\n    Looking for IT-generalist\r\n\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are looking for a promising programming talent to join our ranks to produce modern financial services for private consumers in both Finland and Sweden.\r\n    You don’t have to be an expert since what we’re interested of is someone driven and willing to learn by doing, and up for the challenges of a fast moving\r\n    industry.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Flexibility and ability to learn new skills and grasp new concepts quickly are a must, not years of experience with certain technology stacks, when working\r\n    as a member of a small tight-knit team responsible for developing both current and upcoming sites and systems.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You would be working with technologies including: C#, .NET, Python, SQL, LINQ, Javascript, HTML5, Windows Server, Mercurial\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We provide:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Chance to work as part of a team, to build financial software\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Demanding and creative tasks\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Excellent possibilities to learn new skills and grow\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Great location at Annankatu, Helsinki\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Relaxed but focused working environment\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your application:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    To apply, just send your CV and salary request to \u003ca href="mailto:info@cfinance.fi"\u003einfo@cfinance.fi\u003c/a\u003e. Cover letter is optional. The position will be\r\n    filled as soon as the right candidate is found. We hope to hear from you soon!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
