      '\u003cp\u003eAino Health Management is looking for two enthusiastic junior developers with an energetic and learning attitude.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eThings you might work on:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eJava/Vaadin/Spring/Hibernate/PostgreSQL\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ePlenty of cloud technologies (AWS-based)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eSoftware \u0026 system security\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eDeployment/devops/system admin\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eWe hope that you are at a point in your studies where you can start to concentrate on work full-time. You don\'t have to have graduated and we support part-time studies generously.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nAino Health Management is a rapidly growing health management technology company with its Finnish offices located in Pitäjänmäki, Helsinki. Our R\u0026D department is located in Helsinki and prides itself on quality and effective methodologies. We offer excellent possibilities for further development and a career track including international placings.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nMore info available from Johannes Verwijnen, Head of Global R\u0026D, \u003ca href="mailto:johannes@ainohealth.com"\u003ejohannes@ainohealth.com\u003c/a\u003e, +358505731020\u003c/p\u003e',
