      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We are looking for a (Junior) Devops Specialist to join Canter’s small but\r\n    growing team. Your daily tasks will mostly consist of server maintenance\r\n    and configuration, programming, and ad hoc problem solving. You’ll be an\r\n    important part of Canter’s agile customer success team where you’ll work in\r\n    close collaboration with more senior developers and customer support\r\n    specialists.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    This role is a perfect chance for a motivated and eager-to-learn\r\n    undergraduate or a more seasoned Devops Guru (we can modify the role\r\n    according to your experience or lack of it). In this role you will have\r\n    room and support to grow for instance towards a more senior backend\r\n    development oriented position. Canter’s product is rather interesting when\r\n    you dig deeper into it and it offers versatile learning opportunities (for\r\n    instance in data modelling) that can be tailored to match your interests.\r\n    In return, we hope that you have an open attitude and motivation to learn.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe expect:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Getting sh*t done attitude\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Basic knowledge of software development (school or work)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Interest to learn and work with servers, IT systems, APIs, and\r\n        integrations\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Fluency in English\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e We see as an advantage:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of any programming languages (extra points for Scala or Java)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of JSON, XML, CSV, Git or SQL\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Skills in Finnish\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e We offer:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Flexibility with working times and tools\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A young, international, and relaxed work environment\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Mentoring from experienced developers and specialists\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Chances to develop yourself and your skills according to your own\r\n        preferences eg. big data and analytics just to name a few\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Low hierarchy environment with a chance to truly impact what we are\r\n        doing\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Super nice and relaxed atmosphere (you can even join our band – no\r\n        prior experience required!)\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Send your application and CV as soon as possible:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://apply.atalent.fi/canter-junior-devops-specialist-11-2018"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n            https://apply.atalent.fi/canter-junior-devops-specialist-11-2018\r\n        \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    . We would also be happy to see some of your projects, so please add a link\r\n    to your GitHub or other. You may apply either in English or Finnish.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
