    description:
      "\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Machine learning is so prevalent that we use it multiple times each day without realising it. And we are only just getting started. At SC5, we believe that\r\n    machine learning and AI will be responsible for one of the largest technological revolutions we have ever seen.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    As an SC5 \u003cstrong\u003eMachine Learning Developer\u003c/strong\u003e, you'll get to put theory into practice and use machine learning to make world-class intelligent apps\r\n    and services for our clients, using both best-of-breed frameworks, cloud services and your own bespoke algorithms. SC5 regularly organises trainings,\r\n    hackathons and courses in this fast-changing space, so you'll always be on top of your game.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Our ideal Machine Learning Developer is a pragmatic individual with a solid understanding of machine learning theory and programming skills to match\r\n    (JavaScript knowledge is a big plus). You don't need to be an expert in everything machine learning (few of us are); if you get excited about ANNs,\r\n    convolutional nets, random forests \u0026amp; supervised/unsupervised learning, we're interested!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Technologies: JavaScript, Python, Keras, TensorFlow, neural networks, deep learning, AWS, Azure, Watson, \u003ca href=\"http://wit.ai/\"\u003ewit.ai\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nWe’d love to hear from you! Please read more about us an send your application:    \u003ca href=\"https://sc5.io/careers/Helsinki-Machine-Learning-Developer/\"\u003ehttps://sc5.io/careers/Helsinki-Machine-Learning-Developer/\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e",
