    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Hi there!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    With Christmas just around the corner, now is the perfect time to start planning your summer!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Futurice\'s summer job positions have been published and applications are open until the end of year. In 2017 we offer summer jobs at five locations in\r\n    Europe. In addition to the familiar Helsinki and Tampere offices, we\'ll have summer job opportunities in Munich, Berlin and Stockholm. For one of the best\r\n    chances to learn a whole lot about professional life in IT, as well as international business, send us your application!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    More info and instructions can be found at\r\n\u003ca href="http://summer.futurice.com/"\u003esummer.futurice.com\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cb\u003e= TKO-äly recruitment event on 14.12. =\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n    For tips on how to create a great job application, join TKO-äly\'s recruitment event on the 14th of December. Futurice will leak our secret recruiter tips for making a great job application.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n   \u003cb\u003e = Meet us at Slush! =\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n    You can also find Futurice at Slush! If you are a volunteer at the event come and say hi to us at the volunteer lounge area where we are offering some\r\n    snacks and comfy couches.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cb\u003e= Get a sneak peek of Futurice =\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="http://ftrc.net/"\u003eFTRC.net\u003c/a\u003e is an internal but publicly visible view into Futurice. It\'s a channel where our employees share the not-so-serious parts of their work life.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    On behalf of Futurice,\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Tuomas Paasonen\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="http://www.futurice.com/"\u003ewww.futurice.com\u003c/a\u003e',
