    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Variantum is a finnish software company established in 2005. We are\r\n    specialised in product data management and product configurators.\r\n    Variantum’s customers have modular products that they configure differently\r\n    for each customer. Our configurators are used to manage this process and\r\n    improve the efficiency of R\u0026amp;D, sales, production and maintenance.\r\n    Variantum’s customers are leading global technology companies (KONE, ABLOY)\r\n    as well as small \u0026amp; medium sized companies. Our goal is to grow into a\r\n    leading international player. Variantum technology has 20 000 active users\r\nin 80 countries.\u003ca href="http://www.variantum.com/" target="_blank"\u003ewww.variantum.com\u003c/a\u003e    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eSoftware Developer\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are looking for \u003cstrong\u003eSoftware Developers\u003c/strong\u003e to strengthen our\r\n    growing development team.\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    In this position, you will be working closely with the leading technology\r\n    companies in versatile and interesting development projects. You will be\r\n    responsible for developing and maintaining Web-based Product Lifecycle\r\nManagement (PLM) and Product Data Management (PDM) client software.\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are looking for professionals who can produce high quality and\r\n    maintainable Java, JavaScript and tcl code. Besides the great coding\r\n    skills, we expect a Master degree or studies targeting Master level.\r\n    Understanding of configurable PLM/PDM products will be seen as an asset.\r\n    However, the most important thing is your attitude, so it does not matter\r\n    if you have just started your coding career or you already have a longer\r\n    career path behind you. The final job description will be shaped around\r\n    your own strengths.\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    In Variantum, we offer you an opportunity to work in an agile and\r\n    development oriented team. As a growing company, we can provide you new\r\n    challenges in the future too. Our work place is located in Espoo Otaniemi,\r\n    which is easily reachable by public transport. We also provide a\r\n    competitive salary rate to our great staff.\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    For more information about the position contact Andreas Andersson (\r\n    \u003ca href="mailto:andreas.anderson@variantum.com" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n        andreas.anderson@variantum.\r\n        \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n            com\r\n        \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    , 040-9607034). Send your application (finnish or english) by email to\r\n    Pekka Blomberg (\r\n    \u003ca href="mailto:pekka.blomberg@variantum.com" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n        pekka.blomberg@variantum.com\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    , 050-3141000). The position will be filled as soon as a suitable person is\r\n    found, so do not hesitate to send an application.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
