    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Startup Catapult is looking for a Full Stack developer in Europe, who knows\r\n    his/her way around GUI, and REST applications with dynamic Front- and\r\n    Back-end. If you are entrepreneurial, business minded and interested in\r\n    building something never seen before in the startup scene, send an open\r\n    application to us right away!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    What we need from you:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Mindset for building something new\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Knowledge of Angular or React (if your’ expertize is in other languages,\r\n    challenge us!)\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • English language skills\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    What we offer you:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Great team to work with\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Non-location based work (work wherever there\'s an internet connection)\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Flexible hours (work when it works best for you)\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Competitive salary\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    What is Startup Catapult:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Startup Catapult is the most significant Catapulting Platform in Europe.\r\n    Catapult Platform is the matchmaker between the needs of large\r\n    international corporations, and the means of internationally operating\r\n    startups \u0026amp; growth companies. Our platform is result based and driven –\r\n    no consulting, we aim for concrete results. The platform is an exclusive,\r\n    invitation only, online environment.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • We work with international multi-billion corporations\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • \u003ca href="http://catapult.guru/"\u003ehttp://catapult.guru\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Got interested in this opportunity and want to know more about it? Be swift\r\n    not to miss your chance and send us an application!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Contact:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Mikael Juntunen\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="tel://+358 50 405 5252"\u003e+358 50 405 5252\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="mailto:mikael@catapult.guru"\u003emikael@catapult.guru\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
