    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003eAre you looking to develop yourself as a software developer? Our software development team is looking to hire summer trainees to work with us\u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003e\r\n        Software Developer (summer trainee)\r\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        You will be working with the designing, developing and testing of our cloud-based software. We work in scrum teams and mainly code with Java.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        You will be working within a team of more than 50 developers, test engineers, UX designers and financial professionals. Eclipse, Tomcat, JIRA, Jenkins\r\n        and SVN/Git are the core elements of our development environment. We communicate with each other both face-to-face and on Flowdock. Our Java-based\r\n        software uses open source components, our database management system is MySQL and we also use Vaadin libraries.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eKeys to success\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        • Basic knowledge of Java, Python or another programming language and experience in coding\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • A proven track record of coding either as studies, work experience or hobbyism\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • Basic knowledge of relational databases and SQL\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • Basic understanding of web-based software\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • Fluency with Finnish and/or English\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • Good writing skills\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWe also value\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        • Knowledge of financial management\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • Knowledge of Scrum methodologies\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • Knowledge of Vaadin libraries\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        • Previous work experience\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        You are self-imposed and have a solution-focused attitude. You take responsibility of your own work and work well in teams. You don’t hesitate to ask\r\n        for help or to help others. As a team member you are friendly and fun to work with.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eInterested?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        Send a CV and motivation letter to us as soon as possible, but not later than Sun 22.1.2017. The employment starts upon agreement at the latest on June\r\n        and the position is full-time. We hope you can also continue working with us part-time after your studies start in autumn.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Our office is located in Keilaranta, Espoo.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eOur aim is to be the best employer in our industry\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        We believe that motivated and happy people are the main ingredient in our success story. We have built ourselves an environment that supports wellbeing\r\n        at work, professional development and work-life balance. We offer for example flexible working hours, good working ergonomics and benefits of sport and\r\n        recreation. Additionally, we hold numerous events every year, including sports, culture and other bigger or smaller occasions for celebration.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003eProcountor Oy – Friendly Accounting Software\u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\r\n            Procountor is a leading Finnish provider of web-based accounting software. Over 19 000 small and medium sized companies and over 700 accounting\r\n            offices use Procountor in Finland and in other Nordic countries. We lead the way in digitalizing accounting and changing the way accounting\r\n            professionals work and companies handle their business. Our product development is done mainly in Espoo where we have over 100 employees. In\r\n            addition to Espoo, we have over 10 employees in Oslo and Stockholm. Procountor is a part of Accountor Group’s software division.\r\n        \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://careers.teamio.net/procountor/detail/form/?id=5c8dda0c-b19b-4b81-9dea-f7b63777010c\u0026amp;rps=202" title="Apply"\u003eCLICK HERE TO APPLY\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003e\r\n        Information about the vacancy\r\n    \u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\r\n            Job location\r\n        \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\r\n            Espoo\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\r\n            Employment type\r\n        \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\r\n            Full-time work\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\r\n            Duration of employment\r\n        \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n            Limited (temporary)\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\r\n            Posted by\r\n        \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\r\n\r\n            Procountor Oy\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
