      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eCompany:\u003c/strong\u003e Euformatics Oy\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Euformatics offers high standard bioinformatics tools for genomic data quality management and interpretation.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003ePosition:\u003c/strong\u003e Software Developer\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eJob Location:\u003c/strong\u003e Espoo, Finland\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eJob Description:\u003c/strong\u003e We are seeking a highly motivated individual, who is interested in putting his/her skills to work and developing into a strong professional. As a person\r\n    you must enjoy a good challenge. The successful candidate will work at the forefront of genomic technologies by developing and refining the next wave of\r\n    innovative bioinformatics tools. The tools will be developed to address challenges encountered in clinical diagnostics laboratories across the globe.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    An ideal candidate will be collaborative, self-directed and possess:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cul\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                True interest in developing enterprise level software in genetic testing\r\n                \u003cul\u003e\r\n                    \u003cli\u003e\r\n                        Experience with Java, Python, creating Web applications, SQL, Linux and/or relational databases\r\n                    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Outstanding communication skills\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Fluency in English, other language skills are considered a prominent advantage\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Master’s Degree in a suitable field (Software development).\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\r\nSend applications to \u003ca href="mailto:jussi.volanen@euformatics.com"\u003ejussi.volanen@euformatics.com\u003c/a\u003e or call        \u003ca href="tel://+358 40 5196397"\u003e+358 40 5196397\u003c/a\u003e for additional information.\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
