    description:
      '\u003cstrong\u003eDescription:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\nStroofy is looking for a junior Python software engineer to help take Stroofy’s backend\r\ndevelopment and data products to the next level. Over the past year we’ve built out the\r\nbeginnings of the Stroofy platform to power our mobile and web applications and started rolling\r\nout to customers. As a Python engineer you’ll work with the rest of our engineering team to\r\nbring new features to life and evolve our existing codebase. Working with data is at the heart of\r\nour product, so a large part of your day-to-day will involve building on and rethinking our existing\r\nalgorithms, models and metrics. We’ve worked with AWS from day one, leveraging AWS\r\nLambda to deploy scalable data products. We’re looking for your scientific thinking and\r\nengineering skillset to make the next generation of our product a reality!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eWho you are:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nExperience using Python and SQL in a professional setting or for academic/personal\r\nprojects\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nUndergraduate/postgraduate in Maths/Physics or other quantitative degree\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nA keen interest in data science, machine learning and optimisation\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nA self-starter comfortable with organising your own work day and proactively\r\ncommunicating with both local and remote team members\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nExcited about the product and willing to help define the roadmap\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eBonus points for:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nFamiliarity with version control and CI/CD pipelines\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nFamiliarity with AWS or other cloud platforms\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\nExperience and understanding of REST (Representational state transfer) API’s delivered\r\nthrough JSON\r\n\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\nAs an early-stage employee in an ambitious startup, you’ll have unlimited career opportunity\r\nand genuine ability to influence the direction of the company and be compensated accordingly,\r\nincluding equity options. You’ll come to work knowing the product you manage will transform the\r\nlives of our customers, as we help their employees work in a smarter and more sustainable way.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\nFor inquiries, please contact COO Olli Leminen at \u003ca href="https://linkedin.com/in/ollihleminen" target="_blank"\u003elinkedin.com/in/ollihleminen\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href="mailto:olli@stroofy.com" target="_blank"\u003eolli@stroofy.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
