    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eUbisecure is a pioneering European Customer Identity \u0026amp; Access Management (CIAM) software provider and cloud identity services enabler. Ubisecure\u0026rsquo;s Identity Platform connects digital services and Identity Providers, such as social networks, mobile networks, banks and Governments. It allows Service Providers to use rich, verified identities to create frictionless login, registration and customer engagement while improving privacy and consent around personal data sharing to meet requirements such as GDPR and PSD2.\u003c/em\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eUbisecure, the leading Identity Services Provider in Europe, is looking for 2 IT/ Software Engineer Trainees with knowledge of some of the following: Java, Scala, Robot Framework, mobile development or IT support tasks or equivalent. Ubisecure\u0026rsquo;s core focus is Customer Identity and Access Management (CIAM). It means that you will learn protocols and solutions like OpenID Connect, OAuth2, SAML2 or on web SSO systems. The platform consists of productised CIAM middleware and API tooling to help connect and enrich strong identity profiles; manage identity usage, authorisation and progressive authentication policies; secure and consolidate identity, privacy and consent data; and streamline identity-based workflows and decision delegations.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eBased on your interest and background it is possible to customize your role. You have the possibility to participate in the following tasks:\u003cbr /\u003e- Software development with Java. We are developing Java-based, scalable web applications using modern, agile methods.\u003cbr /\u003e- Test automation engineering with Robot Framework. Quality is one of the key attributes of our products, therefore we push towards test automation and your contribution to that is essential.\u003cbr /\u003e- Mobile application development (iOS or Android)\u003cbr /\u003e- Identity and Access Management product support; You\u0026rsquo;ll, for example, solve support requests and develop our product documentation.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eWe don\u0026rsquo;t expect you to be a ready-made expert in all of these areas and this is a great opportunity to broaden your skillset into a direction you are interested in. We hope that you have the courage to learn, move things forward and share your knowledge to the rest of the development team. It is essential that we work as a solid team solving problems together and sharing information. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSkill tags\u003c/strong\u003e (we don\u0026rsquo;t expect you to know all of these beforehand): Java8+, JVM, Java EE, Spring, HTML, CSS, SQL, LDAP, REST APIs, Robot Framework, JMeter, Maven, Gradle, Git, Jenkins, CI, CD, Docker, Ansible, Linux, CentOS, Fedora, AWS, Atlassian toolchain, iOS, Android, \u0026nbsp;Flutter or React Native. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRead more and apply by the 29th of January\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href="https://apply.atalent.fi/ubisecure-it-software-engineer-trainees-customer-identity-access-management-1-2020?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email?" target="_blank" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://apply.atalent.fi/ubisecure-it-software-engineer-trainees-customer-identity-access-management-1-2020?utm_source%3Dtkoaly%26utm_medium%3Demail?\u0026amp;source=gmail\u0026amp;ust=1579342565778000\u0026amp;usg=AFQjCNGkfpuxnHNOIYeX3MaVljr7QX-zHw"\u003ehttps://apply.\u003cspan class="il"\u003eatalent\u003c/span\u003e.fi/\u003cwbr /\u003eubisecure-it-software-\u003cwbr /\u003eengineer-trainees-customer-\u003cwbr /\u003eidentity-access-management-1-\u003cwbr /\u003e2020?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_\u003cwbr /\u003emedium=email?\u003c/a\u003eutm_campaign=\u003cwbr /\u003estudo\u003c/p\u003e',
