    description:
      "\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eIn4mo\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    established in 2007 and headquartered in Espoo, Finland, is a fast-growing\r\n    international high-tech company focusing on providing world class Claim\r\n    Handling solutions to insurance companies and their partners. In4mo's\r\n    mission is to bring up innovative solutions to achieve high efficiency in\r\n    the business segments it operates. Most of the Property Insurance\r\n    Companies, e.g. If, Tryg, Folksam, Gjensidige, Fennia, in Nordic countries\r\n    are some of In4mo's customers. In4mo is named one of the fastest growing\r\n    companies in Finland. In4mo has offices in Espoo and Stockholm.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are now looking for a \u003cstrong\u003eTesting Specialist \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe expect from you: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You are able to develop functional requirements into test cases.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You have experience in test planning and test case development.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You understand quality assurance processes\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You have experience in designing and developing automation tests\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Your language skill set includes Bash, Python/Java, Sql\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You have B.Sc. or M.Sc. in Computer Science or related field\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You are fluent in English\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We will consider these as additional advantages:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with Android Studio\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in load/performance testing\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with RobotFramework\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experienced with tools such as Jira, Git and Jenkins\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Above all we are looking for great team players, and ambitious and\r\n    self-driven colleagues, who are passionate about their work and committed\r\n    to lifelong learning.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eIn4mo offers \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    you a central role in building world-class top quality products. You will\r\n    be working in an international and innovative environment with a lot of\r\n    interesting people and relaxed and open atmosphere. As an employer we have\r\n    many good benefits to offer like supported lunch, insurances, massages etc.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAre you the person we are looking for?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If you are interested, please send us an application with comprehensive\r\n    (skills, task description, achievements, work history cv to\r\n    marja.leppanen(at)in4mo.fi no later than 31\u003csup\u003eth\u003c/sup\u003e of January.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    For further information about in4mo or the position please contact Marja\r\n    Leppänen marja.leppanen(at)in4mo.fi, +358 40 451 6225.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e",
