    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        hyper[in] provides a game-changing cloud solution for people who manage\r\n        shopping malls. We provide all the tools for multi-channel\r\n        communication, collaboration and integration between shopping mall\r\n        managers, tenants and their customers. The retail real estate platform\r\n        is used in over 100 shopping malls and made available for over 200\r\n        million annual visitors in malls around Europe and Asia. hyper[in] was\r\n        founded in Finland in 2008 and is a Red Herring Top 100 Winner in\r\n        recognition as one of the leading private technology and innovation\r\n        companies. We employ over 20 employees and have our R\u0026amp;D centers in\r\n        Finland and Hong Kong with authorized distributors in Europe, North\r\nAmerica, Middle East and Asia. For further information, please visit        \u003ca href="http://www.hyperin.com" target="_blank"\u003ewww.hyperin.com\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We are looking for an iOS Developer to strengthen our mobile development\r\n    team. In this role, you will be developing native iOS applications used by\r\n    managers, tenants and customers of dozens of shopping malls globally. You\r\n    will be developing new applications with Swift as well as creating new\r\n    features with both Swift and Objective-C. The new applications will be\r\n    partly developed from scratch and some will be based on hyper[in]’s core\r\n    mobile product. In addition, you will develop integrations to third-party\r\n    solutions such as parking applications, CRMs or big data storages. You will\r\n    be working together with an experienced and committed mobile development\r\n    team of four professionals who will give you all the support you need.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eWe hope you have:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        At least about one year of experience in software development\r\n        (preferably iOS development)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Applicable skills in Swift\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Willingness to learn Objective-C\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in developing RESTful APIs\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Acquaintance with Apple’s design principles and interface guidelines\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Practical software development skills (you are fine with using Git and\r\n        the likes)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Good communication skills in English\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe offer you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            A challenging and versatile workplace with an opportunity to get\r\n            involved in interesting software development projects in a\r\n            fast-growing retail real-estate industry. You will have a big\r\n            impact on how we do things and what kinds of services we develop.\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            An innovative and international culture where you have a real\r\n            chance to learn, grow and mold your position to fit your wishes\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Freedom and responsibility over your work, including flexible\r\n            working hours and remote work possibilities\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            A workplace where wellbeing is considered one of the primary values\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Modern and comfortable premises at the HTC in Ruoholahti\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Competitive salary and a great number of benefits from gym\r\n            membership to massage services and free-time activities\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eSkill tags: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        Swift, Objective-C\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eRead more and apply by the 29th of August: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/ios-developer-2?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://atalent.fi/\r\n        \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n            open-position/ios-developer-2?\r\n            \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n                utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=\r\n                \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n                    email\r\n                \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n            \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n        \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv id=":qs" tabindex="0"\u003e\r\n        \u003cimg src="https://ssl.gstatic.com/ui/v1/icons/mail/images/cleardot.gif"/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n',
