    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We are Fuzu, a growth market focusing service / start up since 2013. We\r\n    just received our latest round of funding and are looking to grow our\r\n    product team here in Helsinki (Kruunuhaka). We are looking for developers,\r\n    clever and curious minds, people who are excited about learning and using\r\n    new technologies and working in a fast paced environment and getting\r\n    results whilst at it.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Prior work experience is of course beneficial, BUT what matters most is\r\n    your willingness and aptitude to learn new skills. Is that you? Our team\r\n    has decades of experience in building products. Come and learn with us.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Our current tech stack is Rails / Postgres / Redis / Python and our modus\r\n    operandi Gitflow / Kanban / Test Driven not forgetting Continuous Delivery.\r\n    Are you interested in having your code serve and help millions of users?\r\n    Can you do Rails / Ruby? Or are you interested in Deep Learning /\r\n    Tensorflow / Python? Or perhaps, you are more front end (HTML5 / Angular /\r\n    React) focused?\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Check out \u003ca href="https://www.fuzu.com"\u003ewww.fuzu.com\u003c/a\u003e and send an email to \u003ca href="mailto:jani.turunen@fuzu.com"\u003ejani.turunen@fuzu.com\u003c/a\u003e for more\r\n    information.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
