    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    For over two decades, NVIDIA has pioneered visual computing, the art and\r\n    science of computer graphics. With our invention of the GPU - the engine of\r\n    modern visual computing - the field has expanded to encompass PC games,\r\n    movie production, product design, medical diagnosis, scientific research,\r\n    computer vision, and deep learning.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    GPU-powered artificial intelligence sweeps across industries to create\r\n    intuitive, predictive services. And NVIDIA DRIVE AGX, the most advanced\r\n    autonomous car computer, is bringing Al to the revolution in\r\n    transportation. There has never been a more exciting time to join our team.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The different Software and Research Groups in NVIDIA Helsinki work closely\r\n    with an international team of hardware, system and software engineers in\r\n    designing and implementing the next-generation of devices and applications\r\n    for visual computing, Al and autonomous driving.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    THE SUMMER TRAINEE WE ARE LOOKING FOR HAS:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Youthful enthusiasm\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        University level studies or a degree\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        C/C++ programming skill \u0026amp; programming (e.g. graphics or Linux\r\n        kernel hacking) as a hobby\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Keen interest in mobile/visual/Al technology\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Clever ideas and a drive for neat solutions\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Ability to take advice and give feedback\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Fluent English\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    THIS WILL IMPRESS US EVEN MORE:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Enthusiasm for Deep Learning\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Great scripting skills (Python, Lua)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Performance optimization as a hobby\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with Linux kernel coding and open source community\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    BUZZWORDS:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    C/C++, 20/30-graphics, GPU, Linux kernel, Android, Al, DNN, PyTorch,\r\n    TensorFlow, Python, WebKit, OpenGL\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    ES, HDMI, VR, HOR, Oculus, Kukko, Haskell, sauna, image processing,\r\n    computer vision, Vulkan\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    HOW TO APPLY:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Send your e-mail application, CV and samples of your work to \u003ca href="mailto:Jobs-Finland@nvidia.com"\u003eJobs-Finland@nvidia.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n',
