    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Hey there!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        We are now looking for a trainee to join our Test Engineering team!\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are talking about a fixed term trainee position in the city center of\r\n    Helsinki, in a nice and cozy office. Length of the employment can vary from\r\n    3 to 6 months, based on your wishes. We hope that you would be able to\r\n    start as soon as possible or during February. We have such a great bunch of\r\n    professionals to work with and we highly value the following qualities from\r\n    every colleague: teamwork skills, proactiveness, understanding diversity\r\n    and openness to new experiences.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    As a Test Engineer your main mission is to build further our test\r\n    engineering capabilities, contribute to the development of our technical\r\n    solutions to address our QA challenges and ensure the overall quality of\r\n    our software together with the team.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Your main responsibilities as Test Engineer Trainee would include\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    :\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Willingness and ability to learn fast, and take on challenges with a\r\n        natural and effective problem-solver mindset.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Engage in a variety of testing engineering tasks depending on the needs\r\n        of our cross functional teams and projects.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Understand the current pain points of our service, propose, design and\r\n        implement test engineering solutions for renewing our service\r\n        testability and overall increase our software quality.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eHere are some requirements that are needed from you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You have a critical eye for quality assurance.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with Linux based environments.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Verbal and written communications skills in English.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Relevant education: Studied, or studying Computer Science / Engineering\r\n        or equivalent.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eThese are seen as strong pluses:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiarity with Relational Databases (e.g. PostgreSQL).\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with design and development tools such as: Git, Agile JIRA,\r\n        Confluence.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in Continuous Integration and Continuous Delivery process\r\n        and tools.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in designing and setting up cloud based (i.e. AWS) automated\r\n        test engineering solutions.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiarity with test automation frameworks (e.g. Robot Framework).\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAbout us\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    At Tori we like to describe ourselves as self-driven, experiment oriented,\r\n    agile, kind \u0026amp; happy people. We value and invest in well-being,\r\n    learning, diversity and we put all our efforts in developing our product\r\n    and company, ourselves - basically all the things that create our own\r\n    special service and culture. We have such a great bunch of professionals\r\n    with various expertise to work with and we highly value the following\r\n    qualities from every colleague: teamwork skills, proactiveness,\r\n    understanding diversity and openness to new experiences.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tori values can be seen in our everyday life. We are Trustworthy, Caring\r\n    and Sustainable. Instead of listing our benefits separately here, we\r\n    promise to take care of our people according to our values and to support\r\n    healthy and joyful work-life balance. Read more about our perks and\r\n    benefits from \u003ca href="https://careers.tori.fi/"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eGot your attention? Contact us now!\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If you feel that we could offer you the workplace and the position in which\r\n    you could share your knowledge and expertise, learn, work hard, get\r\n    inspired, be yourself and feel good, let us know! We would be happy to\r\nreceive your informal application and CV as soon as possible and on    \u003cstrong\u003eJanuary 31st\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e at the latest\u003c/strong\u003e. Apply now!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eIf you have any questions at all, please be in touch!\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Simon Cederqvist (Engineering Manager) simon@tori.fi\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Sanni Moilanen (People \u0026amp; Culture Manager) sanni@tori.fi\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
