      '\r\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                        \u003cp\u003e\r\n                            Kiinnostaisiko hommat osa- tai kokoaikaisesti\r\n                            pienessä ja nopealiikkeisessä softafirmassa\r\n                            Espoossa? Ei pääse sammaloitumaan ja monta\r\n                            avainsanaa pääsee ruksimaan: Angular, Bootstrap,\r\n                            React, iOS (iPhone, iPad), Android, Xamarin,\r\n                            WordPress, Drupal, PHP, Java/Spring/Hibernate,\r\n                            Node, Rails. Jos kiinnostaa tai haluat ilmiantaa\r\n                            kaverisi, pistä viestiä ja jutellaan. Allan Halme,\r\n                            Varpu Works Oy.\r\n                            \u003ca href="mailto:allan@varpuworks.com"\u003e\r\n                                allan@varpuworks.com\r\n                            \u003c/a\u003e\r\n                            .\r\n                        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n                        \u003cp\u003e\r\n                            Interested in working part time or full time at a\r\n                            small and fast-moving software company in Espoo?\r\n                            It\'s never boring and check out all the keywords\r\n                            above. If you\'re interested or know someone who\r\n                            might be, send me a message and we can meet and\r\n                            chat. Allan Halme, Varpu Works Oy.\r\n                            \u003ca href="mailto:allan@varpuworks.com"\u003e\r\n                                allan@varpuworks.com\r\n                            \u003c/a\u003e\r\n                            .\r\n                        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n                    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n                \u003c/div\u003e\r\n            \u003c/div\u003e',
