    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    As the amount of information increases faster than ever and the world\r\n    becomes more and more connected, threats related to information security\r\n    have increased exponentially. We at Vaisala need to be sure we are able to\r\n    secure our and our customers’ information – to ensure its availability,\r\n    integrity and confidentiality. To make this happen, Vaisala is developing\r\n    its information security management in a systematic manner.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Vaisala is looking for a\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003eTrainee, Information Security\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    to join our information security development program at our Group IT\r\n    organization. The position is based at our headquarters in Vantaa. We are\r\n    currently implementing ISO/IEC 27001 Information Security Management System\r\n    standard globally. The Information Security Management System consists of a\r\n    set of policies, rules and guidelines for everyone to secure our\r\n    information. As Trainee, you will be part of the project team producing\r\n    these policies, rules and guidelines for Vaisala. You will have a key role\r\n    in creating the documentation.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The employment is fixed-term, being part-time (two to three days a week)\r\n    over the spring and continuing as full-time employment for the summer,\r\n    until the end of August. The desired start date for the work is as soon as\r\n    possible.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eYour key responsibilities include:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Documenting the policies, rules and guidelines for Vaisala Information\r\n        Security Management System\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Implementation activities of the abovementioned, including\r\n        communication with internal stakeholders\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Active contribution in the project team work\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        To be successful in this role, we’re seeking for a candidate with the\r\n        following qualifications:\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of information technology and its role in business\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of information security is a plus\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Studies on a relevant field, for example, university studies in\r\n        technology, business or computer sciences\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Proficient English communication skills, especially written English\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Good knowledge of MS Office tools, especially MS Word\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Curious, can-do attitude\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We offer you an excellent opportunity to gather experience from working in\r\n    a global IT organization and deepen your practical skills and knowledge\r\n    within the fast-growing information security domain.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    For more information about the job, feel free to contact Ossi Luoma, IT\r\n    Security Manager, on Friday February 3 at 10 - 15 or on Friday February 10 at 15 - 18\r\n    by phone \u003ca href="tel://+358 40 7599 149"\u003e+358 40 7599 149\u003c/a\u003e. Send in\r\nyour online application at    \u003ca href="http://vaisala.com/openpositions"\u003evaisala.com/openpositions\u003c/a\u003e by\r\n    February 12.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
