    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Solve the Challenge and apply for Nixu Traineeship\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="http://challenge.nixu.com/"\u003ehttp://challenge.nixu.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    There is always room for one more cybersecurity hero!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Are you our new talent? Solve the Challenge and apply for Nixu Traineeship.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Are you an Intruder, who has deep full stack understanding, thorough\r\n    technical skills and who thinks and attacks outside the box? Or are you an\r\n    Overviewer, who observes everything everywhere, supports others and\r\n    identifies and terminates the bad ones? Do you consider yourself as a\r\n    Gatekeeper, who builds walls and the gate, keeps the riff-raff out and has\r\n    a holistic view of the whole environment? We need you, Droid, as well, if\r\n    you are a key holder to digital identities and able to keep the environment\r\n    accessible and open – except for intruders. Or are you rather an Advisor, a\r\n    mastermind with a holistic perspective on cybersecurity challenges?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Go to \u003ca href="http://challenge.nixu.com/"\u003echallenge.nixu.com\u003c/a\u003e and learn\r\n    more.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Interested in working as a Nixu Trainee?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Nixu is eagerly looking for young talents, who want to set their bet to the\r\n    100% legal side of cybersecurity. We are looking for trainees to join our\r\n    teams in Espoo and Uppsala/Stockholm.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Solve the challenge and fill the online application for the Traineeship.\r\n    The actual work will begin during April / May and the length of the trainee\r\n    period varies between 2,5 to 5 moths based on business needs and\r\n    candidate´s availability. A bunch of candidates who have demonstrated their\r\n    skills with the Challenge will be invited to an “Interview Event” to be\r\n    held at the beginning of March.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Sounds good? If yes, convince us by Trasolving the Challenge by\r\n    \u003ca href="http://airmail.calendar/2017-02-20%2012:00:00%20GMT+2"\u003e\r\n        20 February 2017\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    and fill the online application.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    START THE CHALLENGE\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="http://challenge.nixu.com/"\u003ehttp://challenge.nixu.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    About Nixu\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Nixu Corporation is a cybersecurity company. We work to improve our\r\n    clients’ cybersecurity in solution areas of Corporate IT, Digital Business\r\n    and Industrial Internet. Our clients trust Nixu in projects where\r\n    developing, implementing or assessing of information security is a must. We\r\n    ensur​e the confidentiality of our clients\' data, business continuity and\r\n    ease-of-access to digital services through planning and mitigation of\r\n    cybersecurity risks.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Nixu’s social media channels\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Twitter:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="https://twitter.com/nixutigerteam"\u003e\r\n        https://twitter.com/nixutigerteam\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Linkedin:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/nixu-oy/"\u003e\r\n        https://www.linkedin.com/company/nixu-oy/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Facebook:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="https://www.facebook.com/nixuoy"\u003e\r\n        https://www.facebook.com/nixuoy\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Address source: Nixu Corporation\'s customer/marketing register.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nNixu Corporation, Keilaranta 15, FI-02150 Espoo, Finland, Tel.    \u003ca href="tel://+358 9 478 1011"\u003e+358 9 478 1011\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
