    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAre you passionate about cybersecurity? We are.\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Join Nixu and you will be surrounded by top notch information security\r\n    industry professionals, who understand the threats and requirements of the\r\n    information society associated with applications and systems. As a Nixu\r\n    professional you will be privileged to work in an important role, building\r\n    a securely connected society. You will find out what happens under the\r\n    engine cover of the information society. It is the importance of the\r\n    mission that makes working at Nixu something special.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        As we continue to grow, we need constantly new talents to join our Nixu\r\n        family. Now we have altogether over 20 open job opportunities available.\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The application period is from 28 January to 15 February, 2017.\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003eRead more about the open positions:\r\n    \u003ca href="https://www.nixu.com/en/join-nixu"\u003e\r\n        https://www.nixu.com/en/join-nixu\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We offer a place where you can find meaningful work, have fun, be inspired\r\n    and respected. We are an international cross-professional organization\r\n    where you can develop your expertise and find your potential. With us you\r\n    will have the opportunity to gain experience from multiple areas of\r\n    cybersecurity and business understanding of several industries.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    At Nixu we believe in the culture of empowerment and we value\r\n    professionalism in all of its dimensions. Our organization model supports\r\n    sharing knowledge, working and learning without unit barriers. We are all\r\n    different, but equal. We offer the ability to balance professional\r\n    challenges with personal life and also provide you a possibility to choose\r\n    where you want to work and how. In addition to professional growth, we have\r\n    a large number of hobby clubs from flying drones to ski trips where you can\r\n    find your potential.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
