    description:
      '\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    In addition, we\'re looking for 1-2 Software Developers\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Who are we?\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    We are a group of ambitious and determined SaaS professionals with a\r\n    mission to build a successful Software-as-a-Service company. We have a\r\n    clear vision of our unreleased B2B product which is highly scalable to\r\n    different countries.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    What you will do?\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    You will join a small growing start-up team and be the first developer\r\n    hires. We have an initial design of backend architecture and roadmap while\r\n    you\'ll take ownership of the product and lead development actions of\r\n    programming.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    You can choose your own development technologies and we will give you the\r\n    needed tools \u0026amp; equipment. The product will consist elements of admin\r\n    \u0026amp; client tool, email server, data warehouse, API integrations and User\r\n    Interface for desktop \u0026amp; mobile.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    You\'re the one we\'re looking for if\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You have an ability to write maintainable and testable code in a\r\n            browser, server and/or database.\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You are familiar with different technologies and eager to learn\r\n            more, for example, Java, Python, REST API, JSON, HTTP fundamentals\r\n            or security practices.\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You\'re ready to have fun, getting things done and experience a\r\n            start-up journey.\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    These positions and start dates will be adjusted to your interests and\r\n    capabilities, whether you are open to a permanent or short-term position.\r\n    We are based in Helsinki and offer you workplace facilities or you can work\r\n    remotely.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    We will offer a first-class salary and superior benefits to keep you going!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    To apply, send your CV and contact. Application deadline 22.4.2019.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Jussi Virnala\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    +358 40 549 3107\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="mailto:virnala.jussi@gmail.com"\u003evirnala.jussi@gmail.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
