    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    As a summer trainee, you get more than a summer experience. Taking an\r\n    important role in the company\'s software quality assurance, you will\r\n    interact on a daily basis with professionals from the most successful\r\n    worldwide brands who trust on Tuxera file systems. Your mission is to\r\n    ensure that the software delivered to Tuxera\'s customers have passed\r\n    rigorous quality assurance, customized to any possible hardware and\r\n    software environment.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTasks and responsibilities\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Design and implement feature tests of Tuxera file system products,\r\n    including participation in test automation tools developing;\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Execute performance benchmarks on cutting edge pre-market customer devices;\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Work in a highly skilled engineering team in the quality assurance of file\r\n    system solutions for embedded devices, collaborating with file system\r\n    developers.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eBackground and qualifications\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Genuine passion for Linux kernel and distributions, open source\r\n        software, embedded systems, and consumer electronics;\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        University studies, close to graduation preferred;\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Programming skills, preferably script languages, like bash, Python;\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Some experience with software development projects on embedded Linux\r\n        and Android systems;\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Some knowledge of file systems and popular operating systems.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Read about our last year summer job experiences:\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Rostislav -\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.tuxera.com/summer-internships-with-tuxera-rostislavs-story/"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        http://www.tuxera.com/summer-internships-with-tuxera-rostislavs-story/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Mikael -\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.tuxera.com/summer-internships-with-tuxera-mikaels-story/"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        http://www.tuxera.com/summer-internships-with-tuxera-mikaels-story/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Check the job post on Tuxera website for more Tuxera benefits and other\r\n    info related to this very position -\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/job-application/?aguid=D1BFA7B5FDFF43E58C86634BD5BFBDC2"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        http://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/job-application/?aguid=D1BFA7B5FDFF43E58C86634BD5BFBDC2\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
