      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eDo you want to be in a business that makes a difference?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are looking for a motivated person to develop our Android application\r\n    for mobile phone and tablet users. The attitude, knowledge and skills that\r\n    we are looking for are:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Motivation to produce high quality solutions and to learn new things,\r\n        techniques and technologies\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Readiness to work with a diverse team and end-users to define and keep\r\n        the product and project roadmaps both on target and up to date\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Capability to adapt to new situations and eagerness to solve challenges\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Android development knowledge and experience with either Java or Scala\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Basic knowledge of everyday software development concepts such as agile\r\n        development, version control and test automation\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You would be working as a part of our development team comprising of\r\n    application and service developers. Sanoste uses modern software\r\n    development practices such as continuous integration, automated\r\n    deployments, microservice architectures and the use of cloud services.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Our offices are located in creative Teurastamo area (Kalasatama, Helsinki)\r\n    with good transportation connections. We are determined to improve the\r\n    quality of life of elderly and hence decrease the healthcare costs.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Join our innovative and enthusiastic forerunner team!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eJob position: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    Full time\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eLocation:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    Helsinki\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eContact \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eSanteri Paavolainen, CTO\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003etel.\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    +358405587444\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eemail:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href="mailto:rekry@sanoste.fi"\u003erekry@sanoste.fi\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
