    description:
      '\u003cp\u003eWe are looking for Cloud RAN development in Espoo:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eContinuous Integration and Delivery Engineers\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eThesis workers\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ePart time trainees\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eSummer trainees\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eNokia strongly believes in cloudification of RAN network elements and is investing heavily on this domain. We have made great progress and are the recognized leader in Cloud RAN.\u0026nbsp; We are living truly exciting times in transforming telecom industry and how things are connected \u0026ndash; now you have opportunity to be part of that! \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThesis subjects are related to Tool Development needed for Cloud RAN testing, Datacenter operations and test automation framework development to enable continuous delivery capability. You will contribute to research, development and maintenance of tools and test automation solutions and methods, thus scripting and programming skills are highly valued.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eSeveral Continuous Integration and Delivery Engineers (full time positions) are open in Cloud RAN continuous integration \u0026amp; deliveries as well. Your main responsibility will be testing \u0026amp; validating that the product under development fulfills its performance and functionality criteria and is ready for commercial rollout. In addition, you will be responsible for development and maintenance of Cloud RAN Datacenter and related tools as well as troubleshooting of Cloud RAN Network and open stack problems.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eIf you are familiar with some of the areas, you can be the candidate we are looking for:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eVirtualized \u0026amp; cloud based systems and high availability architecture in cloud\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eOpen Stack systems\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eIP switch \u0026amp; router configurations\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eWeb Application Development, designing and implementing Graphical User Interface (GUI)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eDatabase systems (PostgreSQL)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eDevOps, Continuous integration (CI), Continuous Delivery\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eTesting skills: TDD, ATDD, test automation frameworks\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eScripting and programming skills (e.g. Python, Perl, Shell or C#) are highly valued\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e You also have:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eMSc or BSc in Software and Services Engineering, Communications Engineering, Computer Science or equivalent or soon to graduate\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eFluent written and spoken/conversational English\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eExcellent co-operation and communication skills\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eWillingness to work in a multicultural environment\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAbility to be a productive team player\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eInnovative attitude and passion for continuous learning\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e You will be a member of a highly skilled specialist team located in Espoo, Karaportti. New innovative solutions and testing methods are highly supported in our working culture.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eContacts:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eCloud RAN Field Verification Engineer: Marja-Leena Lahti 050 4872313 \u003ca class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated" href="mailto:marja-leena.lahti@nokia.com"\u003emarja-leena.lahti@nokia.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eCloud RAN Deployment Engineer: Petri Kaartinen 040 5563276 \u003ca class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated" href="mailto:petri.kaartinen@nokia.com"\u003epetri.kaartinen@nokia.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eCloud RAN Continuous Integration Engineer: Sami Putila 050 5119933 \u003ca class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated" href="mailto:sami.putila@nokia.com"\u003esami.putila@nokia.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eCloud RAN Platform SW Verification Engineer: Juhana Sillanp\u0026auml;\u0026auml; 040 7590544 \u003ca class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated" href="mailto:juhana.sillanpaa@nokia.com"\u003ejuhana.sillanpaa@nokia.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eCloud RAN Trainees and Thesis Workers: Kaj Toivio 040 5608904 \u003ca class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated" href="mailto:kaj.toivio@nokia.com"\u003ekaj.toivio@nokia.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eCloud RAN Trainees and Thesis Workers: Pekka Ahonen 050 5388047 \u003ca class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated" href="mailto:pekka.ahonen@nokia.com"\u003epekka.ahonen@nokia.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e Leave your application in \u003ca class="moz-txt-link-abbreviated" href="http://www.nokia.com/careers"\u003ewww.nokia.com/careers\u003c/a\u003e:\u003cbr /\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e Cloud RAN Continuous Integration and Delivery Engineer, job id 17000001SM:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class="moz-txt-link-freetext" href="https://tas-aluperf.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=17000001SM\u0026amp;lang=en"\u003ehttps://tas-aluperf.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=17000001SM\u0026amp;lang=en\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eThesis Worker in Cloud RAN Continuous Integration and Deliveries, job id 16000008Z8:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class="moz-txt-link-freetext" href="https://tas-aluperf.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=16000008Z8\u0026amp;lang=en"\u003ehttps://tas-aluperf.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=16000008Z8\u0026amp;lang=en\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e \u003cbr /\u003e Summer trainee in Espoo SW R\u0026amp;D, job id 17000000E0:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca class="moz-txt-link-freetext" href="https://tas-aluperf.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=17000000EO\u0026amp;lang=en"\u003ehttps://tas-aluperf.taleo.net/careersection/jobdetail.ftl?job=17000000EO\u0026amp;lang=en\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e',
