      '\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMaximize your learning in our global, fast growing team!\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="http://smartly.io/"\u003eSmartly.io\u003c/a\u003e\r\n    is a humble and hungry team of 120+, building a tool to automate and\r\n    optimize online marketing for the largest online businesses globally,\r\n    including eBay, \u003ca href="http://nelly.com/"\u003eNelly.com\u003c/a\u003e and Skyscanner.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    This spring and summer, we’re looking for bright young business and\r\n    engineering talents to join our team!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Summer Squad is a paid 3-month traineeship with flexible start and end\r\n    dates in the spring and summer of 2017. You’ll be working as a full-fledged\r\n    part of our customers, marketing service operations, or marketing teams,\r\n    depending on your skills and ambitions.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    We believe that \u003ca href="http://smartly.io/"\u003eSmartly.io\u003c/a\u003e is the place\r\n    where you can learn and grow the most during one summer — and Summer Squad\r\nis a great opportunity to land a permanent job at    \u003ca href="http://smartly.io/"\u003eSmartly.io\u003c/a\u003e after summer!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Application closes on March 31st !\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\nMore info and applications at \u003ca href="http://smartly.io/summer"\u003esmartly.io/summer\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Cheers!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nthe \u003ca href="http://smartly.io/"\u003eSmartly.io\u003c/a\u003e team\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
