      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Join us in developing the world’s leading campaign and promotion\r\n    optimization tool!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are a team of scientists, developers and ex-consultants, moving ahead\r\n    rapidly. We are looking for ambitious people to join our journey to make\r\n    Sellforte a global success story!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Sellforte provides a software to manage complex portfolios of discounts,\r\n    promotions and sales campaigns at retail companies. We combine the latest\r\n    breakthroughs in data science with years of experience from working with\r\n    leading retailers of the world. Our analytics enable long-lasting tangible\r\n    recommendations and immediate actions. Typically, a 10 X return can be\r\n    generated within months.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    POSITION\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Design and develop SaaS solution from scratch to global scale together\r\n    with our skilled development team\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Get responsibility right from the start\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Be a core member of the Sellforte team of multidisciplinary talents in\r\n    analytics, data science, retail business and software development\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Work with Node.js, React.js, Vue.js, SQL, NoSQL and AWS\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Full-time job with flexible work hours and competitive salary including\r\n    an option plan\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Located in Helsinki Capital area, currently in Otaniemi\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    YOUR SKILLSET\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Interest in startups, software development and learning the most recent\r\n    technologies\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Hands-on skills and get-things-done attitude with Node.js, React.js,\r\n    Vue.js, SQL, NoSQL and AWS\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Prior experience in web and SaaS product development is valued\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • BSc or MSc Degree in Computer science or other suitable field is\r\n    appreciated\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    CONTACT US\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Teppo Luukkonen, CTO: teppo@sellforte.com / +358 44 3299 345\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    • Juha Nuutinen, CEO: juha@sellforte.com / 400 705 364\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Read more about us at:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="http://www.sellforte.com/" target="_blank"\u003ewww.sellforte.com\u003c/a\u003e',
