    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eMascus - Frontend Developer\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        Would you like to gain either frontend or full stack development\r\n        experience through a fast-growing online marketplace? Do you want to\r\n        work with HTML, CSS and JavaScript or full stack technologies and learn\r\n        from experienced colleagues? If you answered yes, keep on reading,\r\n        since Mascus team in Helsinki is growing and looking for developers to\r\n        grow with them!\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        As Mascus’ web development team continues to grow in Helsinki, new\r\n        talent is needed for stellar frontend creation. In this role, you will\r\n        develop websites and application tools to machinery dealers. You will\r\n        participate in customizing clients’ websites based on their needs. The\r\n        development team consists of nine multicultural professionals who are\r\n        spread also internationally to our international locations.\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        The role can be modified for experienced developers’ interests or this\r\n        can be a great growth opportunity for a junior-level developer as well.\r\n        We don’t expect anyone to know all of the technologies beforehand, but\r\n        having experience in at least some of them will help you to succeed.\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWhat skills we hope you have: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Good skills of HTML, CSS and JavaScript (e.g. from studies, personal\r\n        projects or work projects)\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Passion to learn new technologies and methods\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Proficiency in English\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Our stack also consists of: SQL, C#, Bootstrap, jQuery and Angular, so\r\n        extra points for these!\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003e What we offer:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -An international working environment where you have the possibility to\r\n        travel or rotate to our international locations if you desire\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Support and mentoring from experienced colleagues\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Great office location in the heart of Helsinki (great afterwork\r\n        possibilities!)\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        -Flexibility and possibility for remote work\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eSkill tags: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        HTML, CSS, JavaScript\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eRead more and apply by 22nd April here: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/frontend-developer-13?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            https://atalent.fi/open-position/frontend-developer-13?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
