    description:
      "\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        Are you looking to develop yourself as a DevOps engineer? Our DevOps\r\n        team is looking to hire summer trainees to work with our family of\r\n        developers, testers, UX designers and domain experts\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eDevOps engineer (summer trainee)\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    You will be working together with the product development of our web-based\r\n    financial management software Procountor. Your job is to improve and\r\n    automate build, testing and release processes in addition to building and\r\n    maintaining the related infrastructure. We work in scrum teams and mainly\r\n    code with Java.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Our current DevOps maturity level consists of a fairly comprehensive setup\r\n    in terms of Continuous Integration. We leverage Jenkins and modern\r\n    container technology based on Kubernetes and Docker. However, there is\r\n    still work to be done it terms of bridging the gap to Continuous Delivery,\r\n    and as a DevOps Engineer you get to be part of that process. We’re also\r\n    moving towards Azure and would like to take you with us on that journey!\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eKeys to success\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Understanding of infrastructure as code (also related technologies\r\n            such as Terraform, Ansible etc.)\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Experience with Application Servers (Tomcat, etc.) and DBMSs\r\n            (MySQL, etc.)\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Good understanding of Operating Systems (especially the Linux\r\n            ecosystem) and Networking\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Knowledge of Jenkins or equivalent Continuous Integration /\r\n            Delivery automation product\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Familiarity with Container technologies (Docker, etc.)\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Basic programming skills\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Experience with the following concepts and technologies is considered a\r\n        bonus:\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Azure\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Disaster Recovery\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            High Availability Solutions\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Monitoring\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Container Orchestration (Kubernetes, etc..)\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Do not worry if you do not have experience with each of the areas above. We\r\n    value the will and ability to learn fast higher than a specific list of\r\n    technologies on your CV.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            An opportunity to have a huge impact on our journey to Continuous\r\n            Delivery\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Interesting challenges related to scalability\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Competitive salary and benefits\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Smart colleagues and skilled teams to work with\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Tech conferences and other professional growth opportunities\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eInterested?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Send a CV and motivation letter to us as soon as possible, but no later\r\n    than Sun 20.1.2019. The employment starts upon agreement at the latest on\r\n    June and the position is full-time. We hope you can also continue working\r\n    with us part-time after your studies start in autumn.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Our office is located in Keilaniemi, Espoo.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhy come and work for us?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    We believe that motivated and happy people are the main ingredient in our\r\n    success story. We have built ourselves an environment that supports\r\n    wellbeing at work, professional development and work-life balance. We offer\r\n    for example flexible working hours, good working ergonomics and benefits of\r\n    sport and recreation. Additionally, we hold many events every year,\r\n    including sports, culture and other bigger or smaller occasions for\r\n    celebration. Fast growing company with international endeavors provides\r\n    good opportunities for professional learning and career development. Our\r\n    recently renovated office is very pleasant environment to spend your days\r\n    working.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        Accountor Finago is a Nordic provider of financial management services.\r\n        Our cloud-based solutions, Procountor and Tikon, serve over 120 000\r\n        companies and 1 400 accounting offices in Finland, Sweden, Norway and\r\n        Denmark. We are also market leaders in the field of financial\r\n        management. Overall, we employ nearly 300 experts in for example\r\n        financial management, software development and sales.\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003eAccountor Finago is a part of Accountor Group. \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca\u003ehttps://accountor.emply.net/recruitment/vacancyApply.aspx?publishingId=7b555a44-f589-4618-a6ba-804affdaaf8e\u0026languageKey=en-GB\u003c/a\u003e",
