    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\r\n            Aino Health is a leading solution provider in Corporate Health\r\n            Management. Our comprehensive solution of software, services and\r\n            consulting helps our customers to reduce absence and related costs\r\n            and deliver long term prosperity, increased productivity and\r\n            employee engagement. Aino Health has been helping organizations in\r\n            management of working ability for over 20 years. Our roots are\r\n            strongly in Finland, and we have lately expanded our customer base\r\n            to e.g., Sweden and Germany. Our parent company Aino Health AB is\r\n            listed in Stockholm’s stock exchange.\r\n        \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        Aino Health is looking for a Software Engineer to join their team in\r\n        the development of Aino Health’s core product, HealthManager.\r\n        HealthManager is a SaaS solution that enables corporate health and\r\n        workplace wellbeing management in a new way by helping to increase\r\n        productivity, reduce absence and make change measurable.\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        You will work with a tight-knit team of three developers and your work\r\n        includes e.g., developing new features, look and feel improvements as\r\n        well as ongoing software maintenance and testing. Aino Health’s stack\r\n        consists of Java 8, Hibernate, Vaadin, Python, SQL, PostgreSQL, AWS –\r\n        Java being the core. Yet, you do not have to be a ready-made\r\n        professional in all of these but Aino Health offers you a chance to\r\n        become one.\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we are looking for:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            -Skills in Java (for example from school/work projects or hobbies)\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            -Understanding of SQL databases\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            -Fluent skills in English\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cstrong\u003eWe consider as an asset:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            -Prior work experience in software development\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            -Skills in Finnish, German or Swedish\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                \u003cstrong\u003eAino Health offers you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n            \u003c/div\u003e\r\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                    -A chance to work with meaningful solutions and health\r\n                    management software that aims to enhance the wellbeing of\r\n                    employees as well as competitiveness of organizations\r\n                \u003c/div\u003e\r\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                    -Support of an experienced team to become a skilled full\r\n                    stack developer and a chance to modify the role according\r\n                    to your preferences in the future\r\n                \u003c/div\u003e\r\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                    -Flexible working environment and a possibility to work\r\n                    part-time if you have some studies left\r\n                \u003c/div\u003e\r\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                    -Competitive benefits including e.g. a health insurance\r\n                    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n                    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                        \u003cstrong\u003eRead more and apply by 22nd April: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n                        \u003ca\r\n                            href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/aino-health?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email"\r\n                        \u003e\r\n                            https://atalent.fi/open-position/aino-health?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email\r\n                        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n                    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n                \u003c/div\u003e\r\n            \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
