    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Position: Test automation developer\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Description: I am looking for a person who has good knowledge in web\r\n    technologies (html/css/javascript) and who has a solid grasp of test\r\n    automation for web apps. You need to be able to communicate well with\r\n    customers (Finnish or English) and be reliable. The job involves scripting\r\nUI tests for regression and load testing purposes using    \u003ca href="http://www.usetrace.com/" target="_blank"\u003ewww.usetrace.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n    platform. The job is done in our customer\'s premises in Ruoholahti and\r\n    starts ASAP. We train you to a comfortable level before the assignment\r\n    starts.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Duration: This position is at least 2 months full-time, after which it may\r\n    continue.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Salary: 17€/h + lunch\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Company: We are a high-tech software startup called Usetrace, based in\r\n    Helsinki. Last year we became the second company from Finland to attend the\r\n    US top accelerator 500 startups.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\nPlease send your CV and application right now to    \u003ca href="mailto:arto@usetrace.com" target="_blank"\u003earto@usetrace.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n    and let\'s have a chat!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
