    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is looking for Software Engineer who has the passion for solving\r\n    challenging problems in cutting-edge networking technologies. We expect you\r\n    to have a genuine passion for results and ability to achieve them both\r\n    independently and as a member of a team. The position is ideal for junior\r\n    professional who is passionate about Linux and networking solutions and is\r\n    looking for an opportunity to grow and learn as part of exceptionally\r\n    distinguished team of engineers.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The team\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The position is part of our Networking development team responsible for\r\n    Tuxera SMB. You will be working with a team of extremely skilled and\r\n    innovative Engineers - people like\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bastian-arjun-shajit-1b33294b/?__hstc=169887935.52e9974cb1e448e069ec60b04aa6e1cd.1494338015702.1494338015702.1494338015702.1\u0026amp;__hssc=169887935.1.1494338015704\u0026amp;__hsfp=3275091580"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Bastian\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    and\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mboye/?__hstc=169887935.52e9974cb1e448e069ec60b04aa6e1cd.1494338015702.1494338015702.1494338015702.1\u0026amp;__hssc=169887935.1.1494338015704\u0026amp;__hsfp=3275091580"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Magnus\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    - ready to support your learning every step of the way.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your tasks and responsibilities\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Developing test suits for network protocols (SMB2/SMB3, etc)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Analyzing performance bottlenecks, finding and implementing\r\n        improvements\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Debugging interoperability and reliability issues and providing fixes\r\n        in software under the test\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Testing and verification of the new products and solutions.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Ideal background and qualifications\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in C\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiar with Linux development, networking layers\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in implementing binary network protocols\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Understanding network configuration in Linux and Windows\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in Python not prerequisite, but will be considered a plus\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Ability to working in a dynamic, multi-cultural development environment\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        BSc or MSc in Computer Science or equivalent skills\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera offers you\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Dynamic and international work environment, with flexible working hours\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Dream setup: laptop + smartphone of your choice\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Personal health insurance\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Lunch coupons\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Hobby coupons (e.g., for gym, movies, theater, opera, etc)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Relocation support\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    In addition to all these perks, we offer you a flexible work environment in\r\n    which you’ll have the opportunity to work and drive your ideas forward\r\n    using the best ways and tools for you to get things done. We’ve been named\r\n    Great Place to Work for a third year in a row because we enjoy being\r\n    challenged and value continuous learning and improvement. You’ll be working\r\n    with some of the most resourceful, brilliant people in the software\r\n    industry; in products and projects for top global brands. We are also very\r\n    active in tech communities, organizing, sponsoring and attending software\r\n    meetups, hackathons, and other industry events. We support your initiatives\r\n    by offering you an opportunity to spend 10% of your working hours on\r\n    related side projects, and offer you great possibilities for personal and\r\n    professional growth. We also offer you the rare opportunity to change the\r\n    world such that everyone around you is using the product you built. We’re\r\n    not just another software company, we’re powering all the devices that are\r\n    used by real people every day.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Ready to jump onboard? Here’s how to apply!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    This position is full-time and will be filled once a suitable candidate is\r\n    found. To apply, please click \u003ca href="http://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/job-application/?aguid=A69BF4AD41334BA1BA19DCDE7A1547B7#job_application"\u003e Here \u003c/a\u003e and include your cover letter, CV\r\n    and anything else relevant to showcase your skills.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
