    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cem\u003e\r\n                Benemen is a Finnish new generation cloud-based software\r\n                company and operator which develops communications and customer\r\n                service solutions for Nordic SMEs and large companies.\r\n                Benemen’s solution integrates all communication channels and\r\n                holistic analytics of all communications under one unified\r\n                platform. Our customers want to be forerunners in their own\r\n                industry and in offering and developing outstanding customer\r\n                experiences. We work closely with e.g. Salesforce and\r\n                Microsoft. At Benemen every employee can contribute to the\r\n                growth story of the company and give their best in an\r\n                enthusiastic and encouraging working atmosphere. Benemen\r\n                employs ca. 70 professionals and has a firm financial standing\r\n                with a remarkable 81% growth in revenue in 2018. Benemen is\r\nheadquartered in Pitäjänmäki, Helsinki. Read more about Benemen                \u003ca href="https://www.benemen.com/en/"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n            \u003c/em\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            We are looking for a Test Engineer to maintain and further develop\r\n            our test environments. This includes developing both test\r\n            automation and deployment processes. In addition, your tasks\r\n            include testing, both functional and unit. We have already built\r\n            processes and infrastructure within TestRail for test automation so\r\n            you are not expected to start developing from zero. You will work\r\n            in and get support from a tech and QA team consisting of six\r\n            experienced colleagues to achieve our common goals to develop\r\n            bug-free software. In addition, you will work closely with the\r\n            software development team. We are looking for a person who has good\r\n            skills in Python and is able to learn. We are not looking for a\r\n            test automation guru – instead, we hope you are genuinely\r\n            interested in test automation and ready to develop your expertise\r\n            further. We hope you are able to take responsibility over your work\r\n            and have good collaboration and communication skills. We are\r\n            preferably looking for someone who can work full-time, but\r\n            part-time work can be also negotiated.\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cstrong\u003eWe hope you have:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n            \u003cul\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    Good skills in Python\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    Some earlier work experience in IT, preferably software\r\n                    development\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    Some experience and/or skills in software testing and test\r\n                    automation\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    Skills in at least some of the following: DevOps, Robot\r\n                    Framework, Ranorex, Jenkins\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n                \u003cli\u003e\r\n                    Good communication skills in English\r\n                \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWe offer you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003cul\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                A chance to part of the growth story of Benemen and the\r\n                revolution of the telecom industry\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                An opportunity to contribute to building unique solutions with\r\n                modern technologies\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                A role with a lot of freedom, independence and responsibility\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                A possibility to learn and grow as a professional\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Warm welcome, support and training to get you started with your\r\n                work\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Possibilities for remote work, we offer you home internet\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Competitive salary and benefits (e.g. lunch, culture and sports\r\n                benefit)\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eRead more: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003ca href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/test-engineer"\u003e\r\n            https://atalent.fi/open-position/test-engineer\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
