    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera overview\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is one of the fastest growing software companies in Finland. We are\r\n    a global organization and the market leader in data storage solutions and\r\n    interoperability software. With a growing team of 70 professionals from\r\n    more than 17 nationalities, we have been recognized with awards such as the\r\n    Great Place to Work. Our software ships inside 10 billion devices on the\r\n    market, including smartphones, routers, laptops, cars, TVs, drones and many\r\n    others.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Our mission: to open the way for people and businesses to reliably store,\r\n    access, and share any type of data on any device. We envision a future with\r\n    an infinite number of connected devices. With Tuxera at the heart of every\r\n    device, data is always accessible exactly when and where you want it to be.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is looking for Android Developer to work on an exciting project with\r\n    a new customer. You will participate in the design and implementation of\r\n    Tuxera’s cutting edge interoperability applications for the latest Android\r\n    phones. The position is ideal for someone interested to grow their\r\n    expertise in mixing hardware and software.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The team\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The position is part of our Tuxera Prototyping Division team. You will be\r\n    working as part of extremely skilled and innovative team of Engineers,\r\n    ready to support your learning every step of the way. Please take a look at\r\n    some of the team members here:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/agust%C3%AD-pellicer-74375b137/"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            Agusti\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003ca href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/peng-liu/" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n            Peng\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your tasks and responsibilities\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Work on the design and implementation Tuxera’s Android apps\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Testing of the apps\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Ideal background and qualifications\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in shipping native Android applications, especially in\r\n        categories such as entertainment, media \u0026amp; video, and music \u0026amp;\r\n        audio\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with media streaming technologies (UPnP, DLNA, AirPlay,\r\n        Chromecast) and protocols used in home networks (RTP, RTSP)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with Java, Android SDK, C++, HTML5 and JNI\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with GUI libraries for mobile applications\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience with multimedia codecs (MP3, MP4, AAC, etc)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Degree in Engineering or Science, or equivalent skills\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in embedded software development on Linux, Android and other\r\n        unix like systems as well as different streaming protocols is not a\r\n        must but will be considered an advantage\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera offers you\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Dynamic and international work environment, with flexible working hours\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Dream setup: laptop + smartphone of your choice\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Personal health insurance\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Lunch coupons\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Hobby coupons (e.g., for gym, movies, theater, opera, etc)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Relocation support\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    In addition to all these perks, we offer you a flexible work environment in\r\n    which you’ll have the opportunity to work and drive your ideas forward\r\n    using the best ways and tools for you to get things done. We’ve been named\r\n    Great Place to Work for a third year in a row because we enjoy being\r\n    challenged and value continuous learning and improvement. You’ll be working\r\n    with some of the most resourceful, brilliant people in the software\r\n    industry; in products and projects for top global brands. We are also very\r\n    active in tech communities, organizing, sponsoring and attending software\r\n    meetups, hackathons, and other industry events. We support your initiatives\r\n    by offering you an opportunity to spend 10% of your working hours on\r\n    related side projects, and offer you great possibilities for personal and\r\n    professional growth. We also offer you the rare opportunity to change the\r\n    world such that everyone around you is using the product you built. We’re\r\n    not just another software company, we’re powering all the devices that are\r\n    used by real people every day.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Ready to jump onboard? Here’s how to apply!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    This position is full-time and will be filled as soon as the suitable\r\n    candidate is found. To apply, please click on the \u003ca href="http://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/job-application/?aguid=05024B6302AA4651B24208C524B7BB6E\u0026ref=https%3A%2F%2Fmail.google.com%2Fmail%2Fu%2F0%2F#job_application"\u003elink\u003c/a\u003e and include your\r\n    cover letter, CV and anything else relevant to showcase your skills.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
