    tags: [],
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003eSC5 Lead Developer is the head of a SC5 customer team. Simply put, you are responsible for our\r\n\r\nsoftware projects running smoothly. You are the daily point of contact for our clients and\r\n\r\nresponsible for client communication. In addition, as the helping hand of our client’s product\r\n\r\nowner, you make sure that our work truly solves their business challenges and provides added\r\n\r\nvalue.\u003c/p\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nAs the coach of your own team members, you lead by example and draw inspiration from your\r\n\r\nown Developer/Consultant background. Your responsibilities also involve organizing project tasks\r\n\r\nwisely among/amongst your team members.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nYou have gone through thick and thin, and aren’t afraid if some problems occur along the project.\r\n\r\nGetting along with your fellow peers is as natural as breathing, and you possess solid team\r\n\r\nworking and organizational skills. You see the big picture behind the small details, and are able to\r\n\r\nprioritize under pressure. You make things happen and are a joy to work with.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eYou’ve already faced some challenges as a project manager or acted e.g. as a Scrum Master. Agile\r\n\r\nmethodologies are familiar to you as well as cloud solutions. You have experience from different\r\n\r\ntechnologies and software development.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Become a SC5er \u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eWe promise that with SC5 you’ll get to jump into a great working culture with truly awesome\r\n\r\npeople. With us you won’t get bored as we have varying business cases to offer, but we also have\r\n\r\ndifferent kinds of extra-curricular activities such as an active climbing club, doodlers, a floorball\r\n\r\nteam. We do a lot of cool stuff in our working time like coffee tastings, have Friday buns\r\n\r\n(sometimes bottles as well) and to melt the bun calories away, yoga and evening break\r\n\r\ngymnastics. And of course, we welcome new clubs and activities open heartedly if you have\r\n\r\nanything in your mind!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eWith meaningful work, we also offer among other things liberty and responsibility, the\r\n\r\nopportunity to hear and learn new things in seminars and conferences – even outside Finland – a\r\n\r\nwide array of perks that are hard to match and a competitive salary. Read more about what we\r\n\r\nhave to offer from our \u003ca href="https://sc5.io/careers/"\u003ecareer pages\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nIf you have any questions, contact our PeopleOps Specialist, Aini Leppäkorpi +358 44 554 7756 /\r\n\r\naini@sc5.io, who’ll be more than happy to talk to you (preferably between office hours, but you\r\n\r\ncan always txt message, whatsapp, snap, tweet or email Aini). If all’s clear and you feel that SC5\r\n\r\nand you could be a match then just send your application to us by clicking the link and filling the\r\n\r\nshort form and we’ll get back to you.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nPlease apply before 31.7.2017 and note that we will start conducting interviews before the last\r\n\r\napplying date.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
