    description:
      '\u003ch3\u003eWhat is the Elisa Talent Program?\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nIt\'s a 6 month fixed-term, full-time program for young talents in different fields of expertise. The program offers\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ea challenging and inspiring job within your field\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003etraining to develop yourself as a professional\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003elearning and chilling together with the other Talents\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ean introduction to being an elisian and the various long-term career possibilites within the company\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nAll of this in our friendly and professional working environment, surrounded by extremely talented and cool people. Our managers know their stuff, and there are heaps of exciting development initiatives to participate in. \u003ca href="http://www.elisa.com/careers/tutustu_meihin/syyta-tulla-elisalle-toihin/?_ga=2.175748002.1619503557.1499266867-867954224.1494322289"\u003eNeed more good reasons to join Elisa?\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003ch3\u003eWho can apply?\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nThe Talent Program is for you if you:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eare a young professional who has completed most or all of your university studies in a relevant field\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ecommunicate fluently in English (and for some of the positions Finnish)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ewant to learn and develop in a fast-paced, exciting environment\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nApply before August 20th. Interviews and hiring decisions are done by the end of September, and new Talents start working in the beginning of October.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nFeel like you\'re up for it?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nWe\'d love to hear from you! To fill your application, \u003ca href="http://corporate.elisa.com/careers/avoimet_tyopaikat/?_ga=2.149672502.1619503557.1499266867-867954224.1494322289"\u003ego here\u003c/a\u003e (look for “Elisa Talent"). For questions or more information, please contact Elisa Recruitment (rekrytointi@elisa.fi).\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
