    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe are looking for an intern for our Machine Learning team\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we do\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Targeting and recommenders (\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r7l4lAtEs6E"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n            tabindex="-1"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r7l4lAtEs6E\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n        )\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Deep learning for Game AI (\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="https://github.com/jseppanen/azalea"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n            tabindex="-1"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            https://github.com/jseppanen/azalea\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n        )\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Something else, you name it!\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat you will do\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Work on production machine learning systems\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Process hundreds of millions of data points\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Launch models for millions of players\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Evaluate models with A/B testing\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Learn from people with years of ML experience\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we use\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Python 3.6\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        ML stack: PyTorch, CatBoost, TensorBoard, MLflow\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Data stack: Spark, Amazon EMR, Athena, S3, Parquet\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Operations stack: Docker, Amazon ECS, Kubernetes\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Hardware: AWS EC2, NVIDIA V100\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca target="_blank" tabindex="-1"\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eHow to apply\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca target="_blank" tabindex="-1"\u003esupr.cl/HAL9000\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Follow the link for an initial test. If you pass it, we will contact you\r\n    and invite you to take part in a brief yet informative recruitment process,\r\n    and you could end up being our next intern.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
