    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\nDear Lucy is a growth company based in Helsinki. Our product is a cloud based service used by 40 companies in Finland and internationally. \r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nWe are looking for a full-time or part-time developer working 3-5 days per week. You can be either a backend, frontend or full-stack developer. You will be working in a team with four experienced developers, a perfect environment for you to further develop your skills. Our tech stack is modern ES6 JavaScript, from a React frontend to Node.js based microservice backends. \r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nWe will provide you with a great workplace in the heart of Helsinki, the tools of your choice, friendly colleagues to work and have a few beers with or join our running club, a low hierarchy as well as flexible hours. For more information contact Rasmus Back, rasmus@dearlucy.co or check out \u003ca href="https://stackoverflow.com/jobs/companies/dearlucy" target="_blank"\u003ehttps://stackoverflow.com/jobs/companies/dearlucy\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nSend your application and CV to \u003ca href="mailto:careers@dearlucy.co"\u003ecareers@dearlucy.co\u003c/a\u003e. Links to applicable GitHub projects are highly appreciated.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
