    description:
      '\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eDAIN Studios - Data Scientist\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        From business strategy to putting it all together, DAIN Studios is a\r\n        smart partner for companies in developing a data-driven organization\r\n        and getting meaningful results out of data and analytics. Established\r\n        in Helsinki and Berlin in 2016, our team brings in an international and\r\n        diverse perspective into the latest developments and best practices,\r\n        and continuously strives to support customers in the best way possible.\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    DAIN Studios is now looking for startup-minded Data Scientists to its\r\n    growing team. As a Data Scientist, you will be responsible for providing\r\n    analytical solutions to business goals and collaboratively solving business\r\n    decisions through data. You will utilize Big Data and machine-learning\r\n    techniques and databases to design, develop, and deliver statistical and\r\n    predictive models for client projects. You consult with senior business\r\n    leaders to translate business goals into analytical use and communicate\r\n    insights back to business stakeholders.\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Dain Studios offers an exciting opportunity to work with international\r\n    clients from multiple industries and develop your knowledge and expertise\r\n    in data analytics with experienced colleagues.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eWe look for:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Master’s/PhD degree in computer science, physics, applied mathematics,\r\n        econometrics, statistics or a related field\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Big Data and Machine Learning skills, for example with R, Python,\r\n        Scala, Spark or Java\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Ability to apply appropriate advanced analytics techniques such as\r\n        Bayesian, regression, clustering, text analysis, decision trees, time\r\n        series methods, and neural networks on large-scale datasets\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        SQL skills and database understanding\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Good communication and presentation skills in English and Finnish\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cstrong\u003eWe see as an advantage:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Previous work experience in relevant field\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Fluency in German\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eSkill tags\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    : R, Python, Scala, Spark or Java\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eRead more and apply by latest 24.02 here: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/data-scientist-3" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n        https://atalent.fi/open-\r\n        \u003cwbr\u003e\r\n            position/data-scientist-3\r\n        \u003c/wbr\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
