    tags: [],
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Whoopsie, looks like we’re growing and need a person who is genuinely\r\n    interested in making a difference in the world of happiness measurement for\r\n    end-user services. HappySignals offers a happy work environment in downtown\r\n    Helsinki and an opportunity to grow and expand your professionals skills.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You should be familiar with admin of Linux servers in cloud environments –\r\n    we are making an insights and analytics service running on Microsoft Azure.\r\n    Our service is built with Python / Django so knowing that stack is a bonus.\r\n    We integrate with ServiceNow, force.com and BMC Remedy so these things pop\r\n    up from time to time.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your job would be to plan, build and manage a cutting-edge architecture to\r\n    cater for our ever-growing clientele – currently we have over 220 000 users\r\n    globally. Also, you would be involved in customer rollouts and helping our\r\n    customer care figure out the tech behind customer inquiries. You would also\r\n    be building new integrations and APIs to and from HappySignals.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    HappySignals you say?\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are a company of four stuffed into a cannon barrel ready to… uh… wipe\r\n    that… We provide employee experience management solutions for large global\r\n    enterprises and expect to grow rapidly.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are stationed in Ruoholahti, \u003ca href="https://mow.fi/"\u003eMOW Stargate\u003c/a\u003e\r\n    (yes, really) and London, UK. Your location would be Ruoholahti and you\r\n    would travel abroad infrequently.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    How do we make you Happy?\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eA permanent indoor job\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \r\n    \u003cli\u003eA competitive salary\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \r\n    \u003cli\u003eLovely coworkers\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \r\n    \u003cli\u003eLunch vouchers\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \r\n    \u003cli\u003eState of the art tech\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eAn opportunity to deepen and expand your skills as we develop our product\r\n    further\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If you want to know more, please contact\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Sami Aarnio, CTO\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003ca href="mailto:sami.aarnio@happysignals.com"\u003e\r\n        sami.aarnio@happysignals.com\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    .\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
