    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Elisa Talent Program: Artificial Intelligence Trainee\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv id="jid538"\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Do you want to join us in revolutionizing future customer service\r\n        through intelligent automation solutions?\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        We are looking for an AI trainee to join our quickly growing automation\r\n        team within Elisa\'s customer operations. In a nutshell the main tasks\r\n        include:\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            finding and designing the best intelligent automation solutions to\r\n            implement in a customer service environment\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            recognizing targets that can be automatized\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            suggesting, testing and implementing development actions\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        We are looking for someone with:\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            ongoing or recently completed university studies in automation\r\n            (software robotics and AI)\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            a curious mindset and a braveness for trying out new things\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            skills to put theoretical knowledge to practice in a customer\r\n            service and customer operations environment\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            willingness to develop and challenge yourself in a fast-paced and\r\n            constantly changing environment\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            fluency in English, Finnish language skills are a strong plus\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        We offer you a unique opportunity to grow as a professional and learn\r\n        from the best in a swiftly developing industry. At Elisa we are\r\n        constantly working towards better customer experiences – here is your\r\n        chance to join us in building something truly exceptional. You will be\r\n        based in our incredibly cool HQ in Pasila, Helsinki.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        For questions or further discussion about the position, feel free to\r\nreach out to Niina Hauhio (        \u003ca href="mailto:niina.hauhio@elisa.fi"\u003eniina.hauhio@elisa.fi\u003c/a\u003e)\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="http://corporate.elisa.com/careers/tutustu_meihin/syyta-tulla-elisalle-toihin/"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            Check out 10 reasons to join us!\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\r\n            This 6 month, paid trainee position is part of the Elisa Talent\r\n            Program, which offers you a chance to kickstart your career and\r\n            develop skills through trainings and coaching across Elisa. Read\r\n            more about the Talent Program:\r\n        \u003c/em\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\u003ca href="http://www.elisa.fi/talent"\u003ewww.elisa.fi/talent\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e Apply \u003ca href="https://elisa.rekrytointi.com/paikat/?o=A_RJ\u0026jgid=1\u0026jid=538"\u003ehere!\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
