    description:
      "\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eDo you want to be part of a great team?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    Can you see why customers need to invest in user interfaces? Do you seek\r\n    for opportunities to learn more with others? If you answered yes, we want you\r\n    to join our team, front-end developer!\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    Here is your chance to get involved in a challenging customer project. The\r\n    primary goal is to ensure a superior user experience. You will work closely\r\n    with our experienced developers and service designers.\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eSuccess factors in this role\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    We are certain that you will master this position with these specific\r\n    skills:\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n     you have specialized in Javascript\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n     you know some modern framework like Angular2, React, Preact or Vue\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n     responsive design implementations\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    We want you to have passion on what you do. Then you get freedom to solve\r\n    problems.\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat’s in it for me?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    We are in a search for an own angle to solve IT-solutions. Now is the\r\n    chance to get on board to build Lempea. You’ll get our support to all your work as\r\n    suits best for you: tools, facilities, co-workers and compensation.\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAdditional information and how to apply\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    Would you like more information about the job itself? Henri Kivioja is\r\n    happy to give all needed details – you can reach him henri.kivioja@lempea.com or\r\n    +358 40 865 9516.\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    About Lempea (lempea.io)\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n    We are all about People Business. We believe that real business value is\r\n    realised only when teams are performing and whole organization is focused on team\r\n    and developer centered value delivery.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
