    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003ca name="_GoBack"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\r\n    Are you a Software Engineer with a focus on iOS development? Would you like\r\n    to be a key member of a dynamic, smart and passionate team, acting as a\r\n    subject matter expert in all things iOS, and being responsible in the\r\n    team’s success?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Dream Broker is a Finnish online video platform company. We’re rapidly\r\n    growing and we’re recognized as a leader in online video communication. We\r\n    have several iOS opportunities open in our tech units!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    See the video:\r\n    \u003ca href="https://www.dreambroker.com/channel/8mdohtdf/iframe/xwozwxhq"\u003e\r\n        https://www.dreambroker.com/channel/8mdohtdf/iframe/xwozwxhq\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eYour role will mainly consist of:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Implementation of innovative ideas to challenge the limits of\r\n            technology, especially on video\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Product development with cutting edge iOS technologies\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Conception and implementation of mobile apps\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Collaboration with designers, other engineers as well as product\r\n            managers to design and implement the product\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eYour profile:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            At least 3 years practical experience with iOS development, any\r\n            applications already published will be looked upon favorably\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Expert knowledge of iOS frameworks such as Objective C and Swift\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Excellent skills in writing a clean and maintainable code as well\r\n            as a passion for problem-solving\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Preferably a University Master’s Degree in Computing, Information\r\n            Technology or Computer Science, or currently studying\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Very good English skills both written and spoken (Finnish language\r\n            skills will be looked upon favorably)\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\r\n            Self-starter, fast learner and motivated team player willing to\r\n            work in our beautiful office in Helsinki, Finland\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eOur offer\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Dream Broker gives you the chance to actively shape the future success of\r\n    revolutionizing communication with video. We have an international culture\r\n    with colleagues from every corner of the world! Our tech team is located on\r\n    the top floor of a modern building at our Helsinki HQ with lots of natural\r\n    sunlight and sea-views. We are highly aspirational, and at the same time\r\n    fully dedicated in realizing our ambitions.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eIf this sounds like you, apply now \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    as applications will be reviewed as they come in and we’re ready to hire as\r\n    soon as we find the right candidate. To apply, please send your CV and\r\n    cover letter to: \u003ca href=""\u003etech-careers@dreambroker.fi\u003c/a\u003e titled ‘iOS\r\n    developer’. For more information, contact Manager, Talent Acquisition Janne\r\n    Järvinen +358 44 346 5867.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nSee also our tech career page and code challenge:    \u003ca href="https://tech.dreambroker.jobs/"\u003ehttps://tech.dreambroker.jobs/\u003c/a\u003e\r\n    and\r\n    \u003ca href="https://challenge.dreambroker.jobs/"\u003e\r\n        https://challenge.dreambroker.jobs/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
