      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Hi there!\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Although the summer game is still strong, we are excited to announce that\r\n    we just opened the application period for our brand new fall trainee\r\n    positions. This fall we’re welcoming aspiring young developers to join our\r\n    Helsinki office for a four-month trainee period starting in October. The\r\n    application period runs until \u003cstrong\u003eAug 31, 2020\u003c/strong\u003e.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we’re offering in a nutshell\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    What: A paid internship at Reaktor\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    When: From October 2020 to January 2021\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Where: In Helsinki\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    To whom: Junior developers\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Apply by: Aug 31, 2020\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nCheck out further details and apply at    \u003ca href="http://reaktor.com/junior"\u003ereaktor.com/junior\u003c/a\u003e!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Cheers,\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your future Reaktor colleagues\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
