    description:
      '\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Headquartered in San Diego, California with a European office in Helsinki,\r\n    Finland, Adtile Technologies is a pioneer and developer of motion\r\n    engagement and virtual reality technology for smartphones and tablets. Our\r\n    technology uses dozens of sensors, which enable all-new user experiences.\r\n    We work with leading technology companies and Fortune 500 brands that are\r\n    thrilled about the opportunity to finally offer their end users the most\r\n    elegant brand experiences via smartphones.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Right now we’re looking for developers to join us at our Helsinki office.\r\n    We’re looking for someone interested in programming with Ruby, Clojure and\r\n    JavaScript and who would also be interested in developing and maintaining\r\n    our infrastructure in AWS / Heroku environments.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You’ll get to work on a diverse set of functionality across all our\r\n    systems. Mainly you would be working on our Motion Store creative platform,\r\n    where our users can build and publish creatives that will get viewed by\r\n    millions of people. This means we also have some interesting challenges\r\n    related to ad delivery and collecting analytics. We’ve built our own\r\n    analytics collection and processing pipeline. The collection happens on\r\n    four continents and it has to scale globally to tens of thousands of\r\n    requests per second. Ensuring our service can scale up to the demand would\r\n    be also one of your ongoing tasks.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We wish applicants would have experience with at least one of the mentioned\r\n    technologies and of functional programming principles. The most important\r\n    thing we’re looking for is general programming knowledge and willingness to\r\n    learn.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Mainly we’re looking for full time employees for a permanent position, but\r\n    part time positions (3-4 days a week) are also negotiable. We can offer\r\n    competitive salary, office at downtown Helsinki, international work\r\n    environment, health care benefit and a phone of your choosing. You also get\r\n    to choose your own laptop.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Send your resume or a link to your Linkedin profile to\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="mailto:info@adtile.me" target="_blank"\u003einfo@adtile.me\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If you have a portfolio or you are able to share your code on Github for\r\n    example, we’d love to see anything you’ve built.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If you need to ask anything you couldn’t find an answer to online, please\r\n    contact COO Annikki Laine at\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="mailto:annikki@adtile.me" target="_blank"\u003eannikki@adtile.me\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    .\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
