    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Aerion Solutions is now looking for a developer to join their team! They\r\n    offer various AirWatch, BOX, OKTA, VMware and Zendesk implementations for a\r\n    large clientele. Technical consultants design the projects and you will be\r\n    implementing them. Your daily tasks will mostly consist of REST API\r\n    integration projects but you will also be involved in the development of\r\n    our internal tools. You’ll work in close collaboration with two more\r\n    experienced consultants who will make sure you will get an encompassing\r\n    introduction and modern tools to work with.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    To excel in this role we hope that you have the ability to work in a fast\r\n    paced environment with multiple projects at the same time. You’ve already\r\n    gained some experience in Python and JavaScript either via studies,\r\n    personal projects or work. We don’t expect you to be a full package – great\r\n    attitude and the willingness to learn is what matters the most!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    This position is a part time job with excellent remote work chances and\r\n    therefore it’s a perfect opportunity for a student to gain valuable\r\n    experience besides studies. Aerion offers versatile learning opportunities\r\n    to match your interests. Changing this employment to a full time position\r\n    can also be discussed.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Aerion Solutions is looking for:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Knowledge in Python and JavaScript\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Good communication and cooperation skills\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Ability to work in multiple projects simultaneously\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Fluency in English\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    What is seen as an advantage:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Experience in REST API integrations\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Skills in Finnish\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    What you will get in return:\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Chance to work in interesting projects for distinguished clients in\r\n            Finland and abroad\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Flexible hours that can be adjusted according to your schedules\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Chance to have an effect on technical decisions and tools used\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Excellent remote work possibilities\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003ca\r\n            href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/junior-software-developer-4"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n            rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            https://atalent.fi/open-position/junior-software-developer-4\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e',
