    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Furuno Finland imports, supplies and provides installation and maintenance\r\n    of navigation, communication and fish finding equipment as well as systems\r\n    at home and abroad. Our product range includes solutions for foreign and\r\n    domestic shipping companies, various authorities, shipyards, boat yards,\r\n    and the dealers.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We are searching for a Software Developer to join our development unit of\r\n    15 members in Espoo. As a skillful problem solver you will be working with\r\n    versatile tasks in the area of marine software development, for example\r\n    navigation, graphics and data processing. You have already gathered\r\n    experience in backend development (C++ and/or Linux), but most importantly\r\n    you have high motivation to learn more amongst our group of experts.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    At Furuno, with the support of your colleagues, you will become an expert\r\n    in marine IT. We are proud of our own unique products and feel committed to\r\n    our work. Here you can truly make an impact on product development in the\r\n    maritime industry. Your final role will be adaptable depending on your\r\n    preferences and areas of expertise.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We expect you to have:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Some experience in backend development, preferably C++ or/and Linux\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Relevant studies in software development/engineering\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Analytical mindset and motivation for product development\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Fluent skills in English\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    What we see as an advantage:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Interest in frontend development,\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Enthusiasm for problem solving\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Fluent skills in Finnish\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We offer:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Possibility to work in a truly global corporation\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Unique chance to learn and work in the marine industry\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            An opportunity to work in an invested and skilled team\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Competitive salary\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Possibility to work with versatile tasks in i.e. graphics and data\r\n            processing\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Chance to receive mentoring from experts in the field\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003ca\r\n            href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/software-developer-4"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n            rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            https://atalent.fi/open-position/software-developer-4\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e',
