      "\u003ch2\u003eiOS Engineer\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\r\nDream Broker\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nAre you a Software Engineer with a focus on iOS development? Would you like to be a key member of a dynamic, smart and passionate team, acting as the subject matter expert in all things iOS, and being responsible in the team’s success?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nDream Broker, a fast-growing online video software company is now hiring an iOS Engineer in the Garage Unit.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nGarage is a disruptive technology unit in Dream Broker. It is a small and agile team within Dream Broker with motivated and skilled professionals creating new apps for global markets. Our focus is on disruptive concepts and fast go-to-market operations and iteration. This is a distinctive opportunity where you can work in an autonomous unit within a well-established company.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eYour role:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eImplementation of innovative ideas to challenge the limits of technology, especially on video\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eMaintain, further develop and ensure the quality of iOS product\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eCollaboration with designers, other engineers and the Product Owner to design and implement the product, organized in sprints\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eWe value:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003ePractical experience with iOS development, any applications already published will be looked upon favorably\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eExpert knowledge of iOS programming languages: Objective-C and Swift\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eExcellent skills in writing a clean and maintainable code as well as a passion for problem-solving\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eWorking experience on Server-Client application architecture and a good understanding of Databases\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eGood eye for implementing detailed UI and motion graphics\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eDeep understanding of collaborative, test-driven, and agile development\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eWe expect you to have:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eM.Sc. or B.Sc. degree, preferably in Computer Science, or otherwise comparable knowledge and understanding\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eExperience in working as part of a software team, high sense of responsibility and a ‘getting things done’ attitude.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eExperience in developing mobile applications as part of a team\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAn attitude and interest for always learning new skills or improving current ones\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eVery good English skills both written and spoken\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eWe offer:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eProduct development with cutting-edge technologies\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eThe opportunity to work on a meaningful product that will make an impact\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eProfessional team of enthusiastic software professionals creating a new way of communication together\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eGood-hearted colleagues, a diverse, international atmosphere and a sea view office\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAn opportunity for professional growth in a unique work environment\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nYour passion for product craft is contagious, you inspire and motivate everyone with exciting product development challenges, celebrate milestones and on-schedule shipments.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eThe job is full-time in Helsinki (Ruoholahti).\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cu\u003eFor further information, please contact:\u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eKonsta Karppinen, Talent Acquisition Consultant\u003c/b\u003e (+358 50 470 5769, konsta.karppinen@dreambroker.fi)\u003cbr/\u003eor\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eMesbahul Islam, Senior Software Engineer, Garage\u003c/b\u003e (mesbahul.islam@dreambroker.fi)\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nPlease send your application letter with CV to \u003cu\u003etech-careers@dreambroker.fi\u003c/u\u003e titled ‘iOS Engineer’\r\n\u003c/p\u003e",
