    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWarmest greetings from Tuxera!\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eSummer Opportunities\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Check out our summer trainee opportunities here:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://tuxera.breezy.hr/p/6305531e8c1901-summer-trainee"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://tuxera.breezy.hr/p/6305531e8c1901-summer-trainee\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    A couple of summer trainee career stories there as well!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The application link is the only channel in which we receive summer trainee\r\n    applications.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eNot now?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If you feel interested in Tuxera but now don’t see a position for you, we\r\n    are still happy to have a chat with you anytime, giving consultancy for\r\n    your learning in our technology or career development. Just write to us via\r\n    the email\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="mailto:peopleops@tuxera.com"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        peopleops@tuxera.com\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    (note, that this is not for application)!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eNot sure yet what Tuxera is about?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTuxera Story\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Get to know how Tuxera get started with a few enthusiasts who would like to\r\n    make some difference:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.tuxera.com/company/about-us/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://www.tuxera.com/company/about-us/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTuxera Business\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Why Tuxerian always feel proud of what they do? Check out what kind of\r\n    value we are adding to the customers by getting to know our product and\r\n    technologies:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.tuxera.com/products/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://www.tuxera.com/products/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eCareer \u0026amp; Life@Tuxera\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Don’t miss the fun and achievements! Check out how it feels to work daily\r\n    in Tuxera from the career page:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n',
