    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Elisa Talent Program: Software Developer Trainee\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv id="jid536"\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Did you know that there are numerous teams of humble experts who work\r\n        with developing a variety of existing and new services at Elisa?\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        We are now offering you a unique chance to grow into a unicorn with the\r\n        help of our supportive and professional team mates. Elisa\'s corporate\r\n        customers\' IT business unit provides and develops a wide range of high\r\n        quality IT solutions and products (e.g. cloud services, healthcare\r\n        services and custom-made telco solutions), while always keeping the\r\n        customer in mind.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\r\n            And now to the best part: You get to choose what you want to work\r\n            on and pick your own\r\n        \u003c/em\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003ementor who will guide you in the maze of code and tech.\u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWhat do we expect from you in return?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            ongoing relevant studies and/or other experience (from e.g. React,\r\n            GitHub, Azure, Microservices, .Net)\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            strong will to develop and challenge yourself in a fast-paced\r\n            environment\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Finnish language skill is a plus but not a must\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Skills in NHL94 (Megadrive) is strongly considered a plus :)\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        We are not afraid of change and continuous development, so you\r\n        shouldn\'t either. Employees\' personal development, excellent quality of\r\n        work and a twinkle in the eye are things we value and cherish at Elisa.\r\n        Flexibility comes with responsibility. We believe in giving employees\r\n        freedom to choose the best way to perform their tasks - whether we are\r\n        talking about work tools or remote working.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        For questions or further discussion about the position, feel free to\r\n        reach out to Toivo Vaje (toivo.vaje@elisa.fi).\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="http://corporate.elisa.com/careers/tutustu_meihin/syyta-tulla-elisalle-toihin/"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            Check out 10 reasons to join us!\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\r\n            This 6 month, paid trainee position is part of the Elisa Talent\r\n            Program, which offers you a chance to kickstart your career and\r\n            develop skills through trainings and coaching across Elisa. Read\r\nmore about the Talent Program:            \u003ca href="http://www.elisa.fi/talent"\u003ewww.elisa.fi/talent\u003c/a\u003e.\r\n        \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eApply \u003ca href="https://elisa.rekrytointi.com/paikat/?o=A_RJ\u0026jgid=1\u0026jid=536"\u003e here!\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
