    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/job-application/?aguid=D1BFA7B5FDFF43E58C86634BD5BFBDC2"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eSummer Trainee @Tuxera\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    As a summer trainee, you get more than just a summer experience - you will\r\n    interact on a daily basis with professionals from the most successful\r\n    worldwide brands who trust on Tuxera\'s storage software and services. Your\r\n    mission is to ensure that the software delivered to Tuxera\'s customers has\r\n    passed rigorous quality assurance, customized to any possible hardware and\r\n    software environment.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTasks and responsibilities\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    You will collaborate with software developers and technical sales experts,\r\n    with strong support from your team. Together with all Tuxerians you will\r\n    ensure Tuxera delivers products of pristine quality to our customers.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Based on your aspiration, skills and experience you can choose to challenge\r\n    yourself in one of the two potential tracks – whichever excites you more!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTrack 1: Junior Customer Project Engineer\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    In this role, you will support customers in getting the best value out of\r\n    Tuxera’s storage software, as well as contribute to improving our products.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Execute benchmark, test and optimization suites on various platforms e.g.\r\n    mobile, network routers, smart TVs, etc.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Provide engineering support to customer technical challenges and queries\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Implement product demos on embedded platforms\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTrack 2: Junior Software Engineer in Test\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    In this role, you will dive deeper into the Linux kernel and file system\r\n    internals and ensure best-in-class software quality\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Design and implement feature and performance tests for our file system\r\n    products\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Design and implement test and automation tooling\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Investigate internal and customer bug reports\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eBackground and qualifications\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Generally, we prefer:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • A genuine passion for software engineering, debugging and solving\r\n    technical issues either on component or system level\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • A Linux command line power user, who is skilled in programing with\r\n    scripting languages such as bash and Python\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    If you are especially interested in Track 2 (Junior Software Engineer in\r\n    Test), the following are considered as a strong plus\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Knowledge of Linux system programming in C and tools such as make, gcc,\r\n    etc.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Knowledge of file systems and operating system internals\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    • Experience in testing embedded Linux and Android system-level development\r\n    projects\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAbout Tuxera\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is one of the fastest growing software companies in Finland. We are\r\n    a global organisation and the market leader in data storage solutions and\r\n    interoperability software. With a growing team of 70 professionals from\r\n    more than 17 nationalities, we have been recognised with awards such as the\r\n    Great Place to Work, Deloitte Fast 50, and TIVI Magazine company of the\r\n    year. Our software ships inside more than a billion devices, including\r\n    smartphones, routers, laptops, cars, TVs, drones and many others.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eNot sure if we’re the right company? \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Hear what our last year summer trainees had to say about their experience:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.tuxera.com/summer-internships-with-tuxera-rostislavs-story/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eRostislav\'s Story\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    ,\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://www.tuxera.com/summer-internships-with-tuxera-mikaels-story/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eMikael’s Story\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://ats.talentadore.com/apply/Summer-Trainee-/jZLLbZ"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        👉\u003cstrong\u003eClick here to read more about the position\u003c/strong\u003e👈\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
