    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eMake your summer count – Vaisala Giant Leap Internship\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Is your ideal summer job made of meaningful opportunities? Would you like\r\n    to kick-start your career in an innovative and international environment?\r\n    We at Vaisala offer you a highly valued internship program that our\r\n    previous generations of Giant Leapers describe as memorable, challenging\r\n    and just a splendid experience in general. Do your future self a favor and\r\n    apply now!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Our challenging and meaningful program is designed for 3+ year students in\r\n    a university or polytechnic with a variety of skills, qualities and\r\n    educational backgrounds. Each year we handpick exciting real business\r\n    challenges for our Giant Leapers to manage. The projects range from product\r\n    and software development to industrial engineering, sourcing, marketing and\r\n    human resources - just to name a few. Our unique approach helps you to\r\n    improve your skills and gain special insight into our mission of creating\r\n    observations for a better world. The highlight of your three-month\r\n    #myvaisalasummer will be presenting the outcomes of your project to our\r\n    board of executives.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        This year, we are offering the following software and IT projects:\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Software and IT Development project 2018: Competitor Continuous\r\n        Monitoring System comparison test\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    How does a summer doing extensive system comparison sound to you? In this\r\n    project, you will install and run comparison tests with different\r\n    competitor Continuous Monitoring Systems. To succeed in this project, you\r\n    should have technical background and capable of installing and testing an\r\n    enterprise server level software and run tests with the system installed\r\n    devices.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Software and IT Development project 2018: Future Transmitter IoT Proof\r\n        of Concept\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    This is a great opportunity to have a deep-dive into one of our new\r\n    products! This project allows you to study technical solutions for bringing\r\n    measurement data into cloud. An outcome of the study is a live demo on the\r\n    product solution. To succeed in this project, you should have study\r\n    background in software, Information technologies or Computational Science.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Software and IT Development project 2018: Evaluating use cases for\r\n        Artificial Intelligence in the area of content, Vaisala taxonomy and\r\n        metadata tagging\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Are AI and metadata your buzzwords? The Purpose of this project is to\r\n    understand how we could use Vaisala taxonomy to tag content in our future\r\n    Enterprise Content management solution and other purposes intelligently.\r\n    You will study and identify other use cases for Artificial Intelligence and\r\n    tools. To succeed in this role, you should have study background in\r\n    Communication and Information Sciences and interest in machine learning,\r\n    data science and artificial intelligence.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Software and IT Development project 2018: Augmented reality Giant Leap\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Do you want to augment the reality and know how to do it? The purpose of\r\n    this project is to learn how augmented reality can be used to support and\r\n    ease the installation of Vaisala’s products. Your task is to design an AR\r\n    solution and to drive the implementation of the proof of concept. To\r\n    succeed in this project, you should have a study background in AR/VR, UX\r\n    design or software development. Strong interest in user-centered\r\n    development and system architecture is also essential in this role.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eSoftware and IT Development project 2018: Vector Tile Maps\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Are you our next generation software developer superstar? Help us update\r\n    our existing basemap styling and production system. You will do a study to\r\n    find a suitable graphical tool to design styles for vector tile datasets,\r\n    convert our automated basemap production system to work with the new tool,\r\n    implement our current styles with the new tool and study how to process\r\n    other GIS datasets with the new tool. To succeed in this project, you\r\n    should have good programming skills and GIS knowledge, possibly through\r\n    studies in computer science or geographical information systems.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Software and IT Development project 2018: Use of Artificial\r\n        Intelligence as a game changer in customer service\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Are AI and machine learning your things? In this project, the goal is to\r\n    create a plan for the use different Artificial Intelligence features in\r\n    customer service. You will study different AI solutions and the business\r\n    benefits of different functions and also the practical data storage\r\n    requirements for these functionalities. To succeed in this project, you\r\n    should have studies in Computer Science, Algorithms, Signal Processing or\r\n    similar University background and preferably practical program experience.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Operations Development project 2018: Redesign of BI reports, ownership\r\n        and maintenance for Vaisala Operations\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Are you interested in Business Intelligence and its possibilities? The\r\n    purpose of this project is to create new structure for BI reports in our\r\n    Operations unit and improve Vaisala’s reporting system together with report\r\n    owners and BI development team. To succeed in this project, you should have\r\n    IT studies or analytical studies and practical IT skills.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We appreciate our Giant Leapers and treat them as our own right from the\r\n    get-go. The open and supportive atmosphere makes it easy to enjoy your\r\n    summer with us. We don’t expect you to have all the answers but we hope you\r\n    have lots of questions.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    So if you are ready to work hard, do your best and take this leap with us,\r\n    see our projects for the upcoming summer and pick yours! We invite 20\r\n    bright and motivated young talents to Helsinki, Finland or to the United\r\n    States, in Boulder, Colorado. Learn more about the program and project\r\n    details on \u003ca href="https://www.facebook.com/VaisalaGiantLeap/"\u003eGiant Leap Facebook \u003c/a\u003e and\r\n    web page and \r\n    \u003ca href="https://careers.peopleclick.eu.com/careerscp/client_vaisala/external/results/searchResult.html"\u003esubmit \u003c/a\u003e your application before February\r\n    the 11th. Come as you are as long as you’re curious!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
