    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Often the hardest part of a summer job is leaving behind all your new\r\n    buddies that you\'ve made over the summer. What if you didn\'t have to worry\r\n    about when, if ever, you\'ll see your buddies again? What if you could stay\r\n    permanently instead and continue working part-time while continuing your\r\n    studies?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Dream Broker is currently in the search for awesome software engineers that\r\n    really understand what makes great software tick. You keep your finger on\r\n    the pulse with the latest technologies, want to learn new things and\r\n    challenge yourself constantly. If you’re a bit unsure of your technical\r\n    prowess, no worries, you can test how you hold up against our standards by\r\n    doing the Code Challenge at\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://challenge.dreambroker.jobs/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://challenge.dreambroker.jobs/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    . The challenge is designed to be practical, so your success in the\r\n    challenge resonates quite closely with how you would perform at Dream\r\n    Broker.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Dream Broker is a Finnish software house that currently has one universally\r\n    acclaimed product on the market. We’ve been in business for approximately\r\n    10 years and have offices in the Nordics, Netherlands and Germany, where we\r\n    opened our office in January of 2018. We’re growing all the time so now is\r\n    your chance to join a growth company in the literal meaning of the word.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n        For more information please contact Talent Acquisition Consultant\r\n        Rasmus Hietanen (+358 50 5711 626, rasmus.hietanen@dreambroker.fi).\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
