      '\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFrontend Developer\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eToken Terminal is a platform that aggregates financial data on leading blockchains and decentralized applications (dapps). Our aim is to provide access to standardized metrics that enable users to easily quantify and compare the performance of different blockchains and decentralized applications.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAbout the job\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAs a Frontend Developer you will be developing UX / UI experiences that help Token Terminal reach the following business goals:\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eIncrease website users\u0026rsquo; satisfaction and retention\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eExpand our existing end-customer product offering\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOur frontend stack\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eTypeScript\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eReact\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eweb3.js\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eGraphQL\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat you\u0026rsquo;ll be working on as a Front Developer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eWork together with our product and design people to create delightful end user experiences.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eOptimize website speed and mobile capabilities\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eUse crypto-native technologies to expand our product offering\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat we are looking for\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eFluency in React and TypeScript\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eImpeccable attention to detail\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003ePrior experience in doing UX / UI development work\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBonus points\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eBasic understanding of Ethereum and cryptocurrencies\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003ePrior experience in working with GraphQL\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eContact\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eIf you are interested about this position, please send an informal application via email to \u003ca href="mailto:robert@tokenterminal.xyz"\u003erobert@tokenterminal.xyz\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e Also, check out our site for cool charts (\u003ca href="https://www.tokenterminal.com/"\u003ehttps://www.tokenterminal.com/\u003c/a\u003e) and our Twitter for daily insights (\u003ca href="https://twitter.com/tokenterminal"\u003ehttps://twitter.com/tokenterminal\u003c/a\u003e).',
