    description:
      '\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Fluent is specialised in mobile solutions for enterprise resource planning\r\n    and work management. Our products enable diverse data collection through\r\n    mobile devices as well as analysing and transferring data between systems.\r\n    Fluent produces solutions for mobile work management, digitalizing\r\n    processes and reporting. Our clients operate in road maintenance, property\r\n    maintenance, sanitation, and construction industries. Fluent Kunto product\r\n    line is the market leader in road and street maintenance in Finland. We\r\n    have offices in Joensuu and Espoo.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Fluent Progress is now looking for a Frontend Developer\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    to strengthen the team and to contribute to the company’s growth also\r\n    internationally! If you’d like to be a part of an agile team of developers\r\n    boosting infrastructure maintenance by creating top-class digital tools,\r\n    this might be your spot.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    In this role your tasks include further developing the two main product\r\n    families (\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.fluentprogress.fi/en/solution-areas/construction"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Fluent Construction\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    and\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.fluentprogress.fi/en/solution-areas/infrastructure"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Fluent Kunto\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    ) and the client assignments. You will work closely with other developers\r\n    and a graphic designer and you will have a strong impact on the visuality\r\n    and UX of the products. You will create new features and functionalities as\r\n    well as develop further the existing ones.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    This role adapts to your abilities - you get to shine in the things you are\r\n    at your best and develop where you still want to improve yourself. As an\r\n    ideal candidate, you understand users and usability and have a sensibility\r\n    for visual detail. You have a good knowledge of web technologies\r\n    (JavaScript and some modern framework) and are motivated to learn more. We\r\n    believe that new skills will be learned and old ones will be deepened while\r\n    working. Nevertheless, we are especially excited if you have some\r\n    experience also in Redux and/or TypeScript.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    We hope that you have:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Understanding\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            of the user interface and usability and have a sensibility for\r\n            visual detail\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Skills\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            in JavaScript and some modern framework (e.g. React)\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        A\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            few years of relevant work experience\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Fluent\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            communication skills in English\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    We are happy if you also have:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Skills\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            in Redux and/or TypeScript\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Finnish\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            language skills\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    We can offer you:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        A\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            position in a secure, profitably growing software company. We\r\n            create digital services which improve the lives of thousands of\r\n            citizens every day.\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Possibility\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            to grow professionally and develop your skills - with us you get to\r\n            work according to your passion and interests and role can be\r\n            adjusted now and in the future for your preferences\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        The\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            chance to work in a team of talented professionals with flexible\r\n            working hours and a possibility to work partly remotely\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Culture\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            and sport benefit, extensive health insurance and company\r\n            healthcare as well as accident insurance\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Modern\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            facilities and social events to improve your wellbeing at work\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Got interested? Please submit your CV or share your LinkedIn-profile (cover\r\n    letter optional) by latest 15th of June via our application system here:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://emp.jobylon.com/applications/jobs/85751/create/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://emp.jobylon.com/applications/jobs/85751/create/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    . Feel free to mention your salary request, possible GitHub (or similar)\r\n    profile and possible starting date in your application documents. Remember\r\n    to use the application system, we do not accept applications by email. In\r\n    this position you will be employed directly to Fluent Progress.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    You can familiarize yourself with Fluent Progress here:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.fluentprogress.fi/en/home"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://www.fluentprogress.fi/en/home\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    . For more information about the recruitment process contact aTalent’s\r\n    Recruitment Manager Miili Reponen (+358 50 475 4889, miili.reponen(at)\r\n    \u003ca href="http://atalent.fi" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"\u003e\r\n        atalent.fi\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    ).\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n',
