    tags: [],
    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We at Dream Broker still think that the hardest part of a summer job is\r\n    leaving behind all your new buddies that you’ve made over the summer. What\r\n    if you didn’t have to worry about when, if ever, you’ll see your buddies\r\n    again? What if you could stay permanently instead and continue working\r\n    part-time while continuing your studies?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Sounds great, doesn’t it? You’re in luck because Dream Broker is currently\r\n    in the search for awesome software engineers that really understand what\r\n    makes great software tick. You keep your finger on the pulse with the\r\n    latest technologies, want to learn new things and challenge yourself\r\n    constantly. We know, these are a given for all the great, budding\r\n    developers at TKO-äly, but nonetheless we felt the need to emphasize these\r\n    traits as Dream Broker really is on the forefront of innovation.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If you’re a bit unsure of your technical prowess, no worries, you can test\r\n    how you hold up against our standards by doing the Code Challenge at\r\n    https://challenge.dreambroker.jobs/. The challenge is designed to be\r\n    practical, so your success in the challenge resonates quite closely with\r\n    how you would perform at Dream Broker.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Dream Broker is a Finnish software house that currently has one universally\r\n    acclaimed product on the market. We’ve been in business for approximately\r\n    10 years and have offices in the Nordics, Netherlands and Germany, where we\r\n    opened our office in January of 2018. We’re growing fast so now is your\r\n    chance to join a growth company in the literal meaning of the word.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    For more information you can contact Talent Acquisition Consultant Rasmus\r\n    Hietanen (+358 50 5711 626,\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="mailto:rasmus.hietanen@dreambroker.fi"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        rasmus.hietanen@dreambroker.fi\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    ).\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
