    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        Do you enjoy solving complex problems and would have fun working with\r\n        enormous amounts of streamed game play data? Are you passionate about\r\n        gaming? Kamu is now looking for Machine Learning Engineer to join their\r\n        constantly growing team!\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003e \u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\r\n            \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eKey Tasks:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Develop new algorithms to detect cheaters in online multiplayer\r\n            games\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Bring your ideas to life from concepts to production-ready models\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Work with large amounts of data from real-time data streams\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWhat we offer:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Challenging work with great opportunities to learn and apply your\r\n            skills\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            International work with trips to customers and conferences\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            An opportunity to become part of industry groups and collaborate\r\n            with the great minds at many of our varying partner organizations\r\n            in the gaming industry\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Freedom to do your work when and how you like, as long as it is\r\n            done well\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Excellent insurance coverage, with private health and dental care\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Relaxed and flexible working environment at our awesome office\r\n            space in Ruoholahti\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eQualifications:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Wide knowledge of machine learning related algorithms\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Practical experience with machine learning frameworks and tools\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Good coding skills in Python\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Creative mind to come up with new solutions to solve complex\r\n            problems\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Excellent communication skills in order to work together as a part\r\n            of the team\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Attention to detail and at all times being critical to your work\r\n            for improvement\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWe consider as a plus:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Machine learning related hobby projects to show off\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Skills in programming languages of your choice\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Passionate multiplayer PC gamer\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Understanding of game cheats\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        Apply now or by the \u003cstrong\u003e14th of May!\u003c/strong\u003e Read more and apply\r\n        here:\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://atalent.fi/avoimet-tyopaikat/machine-learning-engineer/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://atalent.fi/avoimet-tyopaikat/machine-learning-engineer/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
