    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Cloubi is now expanding their team with Full Stack Developers! In this\r\n    role, you will be working with our software Cloubi, a tool used for\r\n    designing digital learning materials. You will be involved in designing,\r\n    testing, and implementing the tool either in projects for our clients or in\r\n    our internal product development. Since this role can be tailored according\r\n    to your wishes and skills the tasks vary from user interface design to\r\n    handling the databases.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    Our development team is divided into our Helsinki and Tampere offices. The\r\n    team in Tampere consists of senior developers and the team in Helsinki of\r\n    developers that are at an earlier stage of their career. You can choose\r\n    which office you wish to work in. In this role, you get to work with the\r\n    state-of-the-art digital learning materials that utilize analytics,\r\n    adaptive contents, and gamification. As a highly growing international\r\n    company, we have already set a foot in Europe and are planning to expand to\r\n    the US market.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    We hope that you are already at the end of you studies in a relevant field\r\n    of study. You can also be a more experienced developer since this role\r\n    provides a lot of chances to grow and have an effect on our technical\r\n    solutions. What we value the most is experience working with Java but we\r\n    hope you to have knowledge in web technologies such as JavaScript, HTML5\r\n    and CSS. We appreciate good collaboration and communication skills.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe look for:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Skills in Java, JavaScript, HTML5, and CSS\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Knowledge in relational databases\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Good collaboration and communication skills\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Fluency in English\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat is seen as an advantage:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Experience building user interfaces with VUE\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Skills in JavaScript libraries (eg. JQuery and RequireJS)\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Knowledge in Linux, Tomcat and Nginx\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Skills in Finnish\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eAs part of our team, you will have:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Interesting tasks in the field of digital learning either in client\r\n            projects or product development\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            The chance to get responsibility and be promoted in a more\r\n            challenging position or management role over time\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Flexibility in work hours and the chance to work remotely\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Supportive team in a growing company\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    Are you the person we are looking for? Take the first step to joining our\r\n    team and send your CV and application letter in PDF form to:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://apply.atalent.fi/cloubi-full-stack-developers-7-2018"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://apply.atalent.fi/cloubi-full-stack-developers-7-2018\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    no later than \u003cstrong\u003eTuesday 14th of August\u003c/strong\u003e. Please also attach\r\n    your portfolio or GitHub profile with relevant references of your projects.\r\n    Please note that we go through the applications already during the\r\n    application period so apply fast!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
