    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\nFinnish: required\r\nPoisiton: Backend Developer | 44-69K\r\nType: full-time\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eFrends Technology is\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        looking for a Backend Developer to work in integration consulting team\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhy us?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        We work in our \u003cstrong\u003eown small teams\u003c/strong\u003e which increases team\r\n        spirit.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        We have our \u003cstrong\u003eown integration platform\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003ca href="https://frends.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"\u003e\r\n            \u003cstrong\u003eFrends\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n        - the product development team is close, responsive and listens to\r\n        wishes. As a result, development is fast and you get help quickly with\r\n        any challenges.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        We are \u003cstrong\u003estable and modern house\u003c/strong\u003e - you get to evolve and\r\n        develop new, no maintenance of old Legacy\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        In our wide range portfolio of\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="https://frends.com/customers"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n            rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            clients\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n        , you can find nationally and internationally known companies in\r\n        various industries that will lead you to\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n            interesting and meaningful projects and various technologies.\r\n        \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe offer\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        competitive salary of \u003cstrong\u003e44-69K\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        depending on experience\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        the opportunity to further develop and expand your skills\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        flexible working times and locations\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        an employer who supports in various life situations\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        safe and stable workplace\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        skilled co-workers and a supporting supervisor and team\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        low hierarchy and flexible and relaxed organizational culture\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        comprehensive personnel benefits (e.g., learning platforms, extensive\r\n        occupational health care and health insurance, lunch benefit, sport\r\n        \u0026amp; cultural benefit vouchers, cultural and sports club, sick child\r\n        care benefit)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eTechnologies\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Our specialty is our own low-code, hybrid integration platform\r\n    \u003ca href="https://frends.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"\u003e\r\n        Frends\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    , which we often use in our projects. In our work, you will get to use also\r\n    Azure\'s various technologies, such as Machine Learning and Data Factory.\r\n    The magic words for success are REST, JSON, XML, XSLT, and SQL. In\r\n    addition, knowledge of API architectures, API Management, GraphQL, and LINQ\r\n    are things we value - which you’ll also get to learn.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eInterested to join us?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If this piqued your interest, we hope you will contact us via the\r\n    application form or by emailing Elina:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="mailto:elina.salo@frends.com"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        elina.salo@frends.com\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    .\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eNo CV is needed\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    - more important is to have a discussion with you.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://careers.frends.com/blog/posts/43161-frends-recruitment-process"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eOur recruitment process\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    is smooth, transparent, flexible, conversational and informative. You will\r\n    meet a team supervisor and team member through Teams - no need to travel\r\n    and you have the opportunity to discuss about the everyday life. We map out\r\n    your technical skills by a discussion with you or through a technical\r\n    assignment which you can do at a time that suits you best. We will make the\r\n    decision fast from our side.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eOther related to the job\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul type="disc"\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        We offer flexibility in working hours and location in Finland.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        The start is flexible during according to your situation.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Please note that this role requires fluent Finnish.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e',
