    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The Junior Software Developer role is our entry level position, where\r\n    people can grow and learn before choosing what area to specialize to. In\r\n    this role, internally referred to as Technical Project Manager, you will\r\n    perform technical tasks developing our software and tailoring it to our\r\n    customers’ needs. Depending on your previous experience and language\r\n    skills, you will have the chance to participate in implementations also in\r\n    markets outside Finland.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    As we are growing fast we are constantly looking for new talent. For your\r\n    information, candidates who have applied to this position can also be\r\n    considered to other positions within the Solutions team e.g. customer\r\n    support, infra, internal technical support, release management and internal\r\n    tools.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe value the following aspects in our candidates:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cul\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                You have an interest in working in international projects\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                You know your way around at least one coding language (knowing\r\n                Java/Ruby/JRuby/JavaScript is seen as an advantage)\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                You have the interest and enthusiasm to solve customers’\r\n                problems\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                You are not afraid of large amounts of data and analysis\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                You are fluent in English. Also, fluency in other European\r\n                languages is an advantage (Finnish, Italian, Swedish, French)\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                You have a university degree or you are pursuing one\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eWe offer you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n        \u003cul\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                A young, international and relaxed work environment in a flat\r\n                organization\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Challenging and varied tasks with the possibility to choose\r\n                your own tools\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                Lots of sporting options: Gym, yoga, floorball, badminton…\r\n                We’ve also got a brewing club!\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\r\n                And at RELEX we appreciate your work and your skills\r\n                \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n                    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n                \u003c/div\u003e\r\n            \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\r\nSounds like a match for you? Submit your application in PDF by        \u003cstrong\u003e20\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e.8.2018\u003c/strong\u003e:\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="https://apply.atalent.fi/relex-junior-software-developer-8-2018"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n            rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            https://apply.atalent.fi/relex-junior-software-developer-8-2018\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n        .\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
