    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cem\u003e\r\n            Carus is a global supplier of information systems to the travel and\r\n            transport industry. With a customer base of corporate, state and\r\n            privately owned companies, we build and support systems that are\r\n            critical to the operations of ferry, cruise, port and leisure\r\n            businesses across the world.\r\n        \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Carus is looking for a Jr. Full Stack Developer to join their agile\r\n    software development team in Espoo. In this position you will be working\r\n    with Carus’ main product CarRes, a business-critical reservations system\r\n    for our global passenger shipping customers.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cstrong\u003eCarus is looking for someone with:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            University degree or on-going studies from a relevant field, e.g.\r\n            computer science, information technology, mathematics or equivalent\r\n            or comparable experience\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            A junior level understanding of both backend and frontend\r\n            programming for web solutions\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            A junior level skill set with relational databases\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Excellent problem solving skills and persistency\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Fluency in English, both spoken and written\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eCarus considers as a plus:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Swedish language skills\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Skills in Java, Angular, PHP, JavaScript, Bash, Ansible or Visual\r\n            Basic\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWe can offer you:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            The stability of an established international company but the\r\n            flexibility of a small and agile development team\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            The chance to take responsibility and have an effect on the big\r\n            picture with your input\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Mentoring and support from more experienced team members\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            A relaxed atmosphere at the office and flexibility on working hours\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            Competitive salary and benefits\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli\u003e\r\n            In this position you will be employed directly to Carus Ab Ltd.\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eRead more here and apply by 5th March 2019: \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cu\u003e\r\n        \u003ca\r\n            href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/jr-full-stack-developer"\r\n            target="_blank"\r\n            rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n        \u003e\r\n            https://atalent.fi/open-position/jr-full-stack-developer\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/u\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
