    description:
      '\u003ch3\u003e\r\n    Automated phishing training and response\r\n\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    HoxHunt turns your employees into the greatest asset in cyber security.\r\n    We\'re relentlessly focused on empowering employees to shield organisations\r\n    as an active last line of cyber defence - and making it fun along the way.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch3\u003e\r\n    HoxHunt Summer Hunters 2019 application period is on until 17.3.2019\r\n\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Do you want to see your code creating real impact on society? How does it\r\n    sound to spend the summer fighting against cybercrime? Join our team as a\r\n    HoxHunt Summer Hunter and you will be contributing to a tool that turns\r\n    employees into the strongest cybersecurity source of the company.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We also care about your growth as a developer and want to help you grow\r\n    into your fullest potential during the summer. Our friendly HoxHunt mentors\r\n    will be there to support you throughout the program. So what are you\r\n    waiting for? Apply now!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003e\r\n        What is the program about\r\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Our ideal candidate is someone who loves to write code and gets excited\r\n        about continuously learning new in the field of technology. Your work\r\n        will directly raise awareness against phishing and cyber attacks and in\r\n        this way you help to secure digital societies.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003e\r\n        When it happens\r\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Summer Hunter program will last for three months from 1st of June to\r\n        30th of August but we hope that after the summer you will stay with us\r\n        as a part-time or full-time developer depending on your studies. The\r\n        timing is also negotiable if that exact slot doesn’t suit you.\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003e\r\n        Software Developer\r\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Have you always wanted to be part of an internationally expanding and\r\n        fast-growing startup making world a better place by building great\r\n        software to fight against cybercrime? Are you keen to grow into a great\r\n        software developer?\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003ch3\u003e\r\n        Data Scientist\r\n    \u003c/h3\u003e\r\n    \u003cp\u003e\r\n        Is your dream to work with world-changing data to utilise its benefits\r\n        and power to fight against cybercrime? Do you see yourself modeling the\r\n        future of cybersecurity? Are you keen to grow into a great data\r\n        scientist?\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Apply here!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://hunters.hoxhunt.com/"\u003ehttps://hunters.hoxhunt.com/\u003c/a\u003e',
