    description:
      '\u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003ch3\u003eData Engineer\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003eWe are looking for a Data Engineer to join our growing team in Helsinki. You will work closely with our data scientist on how to implement new data-driven features for the influencer marketing platform.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003ch3\u003eResponsibilities\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n        \u003cul\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003eCollect, store and process large amounts of data to optimise\u0026nbsp;our platform.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003eChoose, implement, and maintain the best\u0026nbsp;solutions for our data science needs.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003eMake data comprehensible\u0026nbsp;for exploration and analysis.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n        \u003ch3\u003eMinimum Qualifications\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n        \u003cul\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003eHands-on experience with big data applications in a production environment and distributed computing.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003eStrong understanding of SQL and NoSQL databases and data warehousing.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003eExperience with distributed computing.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003eGood written and spoken communication skills.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n        \u003ch3\u003ePreferred Qualifications\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n        \u003cul\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003eExperience in atleast one of the technologies we use at Matchmade: PostgreSQL, Elasticsearch, Influx, Redshift, Dynamo, Hadoop.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003eExcited about and good at solving complex data storage and transformation problems on a daily basis.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003ePrior knowledge of data analysis and statistical methods.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003eAbility to thrive in a startup environment and work well as a team player.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n            \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003eInterest in ad tech, influencer marketing, games, Twitch live streams and YouTube cat videos.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n        \u003ch3\u003eInterested?\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n        \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style="font-weight: 400;"\u003eWe\'re a small and experienced team shaping the future of the fastest growing digital marketing channel. We have offices in Helsinki and Berlin and offer competitive compensation, benefits and great coworkers. Join us for an unforgettable experience building cutting-edge tech in the quickly changing space of digital marketing.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003cbr\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003ca href="mailto:paula@matchmade.tv"\u003eEmail us\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href="https://angel.co/shark-punch/jobs" target="_blank"\u003eApply on AngelList\u003c/a\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr\u003e\r\n        \u003ca href="http://matchmade.tv/jobs/"\u003eRead more about Matchmade\u003c/a\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/section\u003e\r\n',
