    description:
      "\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Did you know that there are numerous teams of humble experts who work with\r\n    developing a variety of existing and new services at Elisa? Elisa's\r\n    corporate customers' IT business unit provides and develops a wide range of\r\n    high quality IT solutions and products (e.g. cloud services, healthcare\r\n    services and custom-made telco solutions), while always keeping the\r\n    customer in mind.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are growing our Public Cloud team and want to give the opportunity for\r\n    two \u003cstrong\u003eProduct Specialist Trainees\u003c/strong\u003e to join us for full-time.\r\n    The trainee period will last for 8 months after which chances are that we\r\n    will want you to stay on board with us as a full-grown expert.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your will be responsible of commercializing your very own product segment,\r\n    working as part of a supportive and (at least according to ourselves) fun\r\n    team of professionals. You'll also have the opportunity to work with and\r\n    learn from partners and customers, and take part in developing our services\r\n    in general. We believe in a very agile working culture where we keep an\r\n    active dialogue together with internal experts, Elisa's production, our\r\n    service management as well as our work mates in the customer front-line.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat do we expect from you in return?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You have some relevant experience or knowledge in cloud technologies\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You're a team worker at heart and do not shy away from new challenges\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You communicate fluently in both Finnish and English (this because part\r\n        of your job is to produce content in Finnish, and if needed in English)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You want to be good at what you do and you enjoy sharing your knowhow\r\n        with others\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You have a strong will to develop and challenge yourself in a\r\n        fast-paced environment\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Previous experience of commercializing products/services is appreciated\r\n        but not required\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are not afraid of change and continuous development, so you shouldn't\r\n    either. Employees' personal development, excellent quality of work and a\r\n    twinkle in the eye are things we value and cherish at Elisa. Flexibility\r\n    comes with responsibility. We believe in giving employees freedom to choose\r\n    the best way to perform their tasks - whether we are talking about work\r\n    tools or remote working.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The majority of our team is based in Helsinki, which is why we hope you'd\r\n    be here too for us to be able to support you as much as possible. Please\r\n    note that the chosen persons will undergo a security clearance in order to\r\n    gain access to systems and tools needed, and this requires either a Finnish\r\n    citizenship or having lived in Finland for at least 5 years.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Interested? Leave us your application as soon as possible! For questions or\r\n    further discussion about the position, feel free to reach out to Ira at\r\n    +358 50 3955471 or ira.keskitalo@elisa.fi.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e",
