    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Did you know that there are numerous teams of humble experts who work with\r\n    developing a variety of existing and new services at Elisa?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are now offering you a unique chance to grow your skills with the help\r\n    of our supportive and professional team mates. We work with multiple\r\n    different integration technologies and software development languages (e.g.\r\n    BizTalk, .NET and Java). The trainee period will last for 6 months after\r\n    which chances are high that we will want you to stay on board with us as a\r\n    full-grown expert!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        And now to the best part: You get to choose what you want to work on\r\n        and pick your own\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003ementor who will guide you in the maze of code and tech.\u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eWhat do we expect from you in return?\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        ongoing relevant studies and/or other experience (from software\r\n        development e.g. React, GitHub, Azure, Microservices, .Net, PWA)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        strong will to develop and challenge yourself in a fast-paced\r\n        environment\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Finnish language skill is a plus but not a must\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Skills in NHL94 (megadrive) is strongly considered a plus :)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are not afraid of change and continuous development, so you shouldn\'t\r\n    either. Employees\' personal development, excellent quality of work and a\r\n    twinkle in the eye are things we value and cherish at Elisa. Flexibility\r\n    comes with responsibility. We believe in giving employees freedom to choose\r\n    the best way to perform their tasks - whether we are talking about work\r\n    tools or remote working.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The majority of our team is based in Helsinki, which is why we hope you\'d\r\n    be here too for us to be able to support you as much as possible. Please\r\n    note that the chosen persons will undergo a security clearance in order to\r\n    gain access to systems and tools needed, and this requires either a Finnish\r\n    citizenship or having lived in Finland for at least 5 years.\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Interested? Shoot us your application as soon as possible! For questions or\r\n    further discussion about the position, feel free to reach out to Tuomas\r\nJokimaa (\u003ca href="mailto:tuomas.jokimaa@elisa.fi"\u003etuomas.jokimaa@elisa.fi\u003c/a\u003e) or\r\nTommi Somersuo (\u003ca href="mailto:tommi.somersuo@elisa.fi"\u003etommi.somersuo@elisa.fi\u003c/a\u003e).\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
