    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Welcome to your McKinsey career!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cb\u003eChange\u003c/b\u003e the world. \u003cb\u003eInvent\u003c/b\u003e something new.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cb\u003eSolve\u003c/b\u003e a complex problem. \u003cb\u003eExtend\u003c/b\u003e your talents.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cb\u003eBuild\u003c/b\u003e enduring relationships.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    McKinsey Helsinki is looking for talent. Our internship program is intended\r\n    for students from every university and major degree. The only minimum\r\n    requirement is 80 academic credits, with an aim to complete a Master\'s\r\n    degree. We look for people with excellent problem-solving and people\r\n    skills, leadership potential, entrepreneurship, a healthy curiosity, and\r\n    the courage to take initiative - a business background is not required to\r\n    succeed at McKinsey.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e Students joining us as interns will spend 2-3 months\r\n    working as integral members of client service teams, and getting the same\r\n    experience as a new full-time consultant.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e One of our most important values\r\n    is to ensure talented people are quickly presented with opportunities that\r\n    use and strengthen their skills and passions. For interns who are\r\n    interested in an international experience, we offer the chance to do client\r\n    work with international teams.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e McKinsey \u0026amp; Company is a global\r\n    management consulting firm that serves leading businesses, governments,\r\n    non-governmental organizations, and not-for-profits.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e Learn more about us\r\n    and apply by going to \u003ca href="https://mckinsey.com/fi"\u003ewww.mckinsey.com/fi\u003c/a\u003e and selecting internship FAQs.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
