    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Meru Health is an online mental healthcare provider that helps people\r\n    improve their mental health long-term by treating and preventing anxiety,\r\n    depression, and burnout.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Are you a self-driven Software Engineer who is passionate about building a\r\n    great product and interested in helping people suffering from depression in\r\n    a concrete and measurable way? If you are, we are looking for you!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    As a Software Engineer you will play a key role in product development of\r\n    Meru Health platform, driving decisions related to technology,\r\n    architecture, security, and user experience. You will be part of Meru\r\n    Health’s small but skillful Product Development team committed to improving\r\n    how depression is treated worldwide by utilizing the latest science and\r\n    mobile technology.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Check out the details and apply at\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca\r\n    href="https://stackoverflow.com/jobs/360868/javascript-engineer-meru-health!"\r\n    target="_blank"\r\n    rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    id="LPlnk387183"\r\n\u003e\r\n    https://stackoverflow.com/jobs/360868/javascript-engineer-meru-health!\r\n\u003c/a\u003e',
