    tags: [],
    description:
      "\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Are you a recent graduate or soon to be graduated interested in technology?\r\n    Would you like to have a permanent contract from the beginning of your\r\n    career?\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    In Capgemini we trust our people and hire only people that we believe in.\r\n    That’s why our graduates get a permanent contract and responsibility from\r\n    the beginning of their career. In our graduate program we will help you to\r\n    grow into a technology professional with a successful career in a global IT\r\n    consulting company. Whether your passion is in coding or designing UIs or\r\n    you are just interested to have a career within technology field, we have a\r\n    career path for you.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Maybe you want to become an ace in..\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eProject Management\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eRPA (Robotic process automation)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eData Analytics\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eFront-End Development\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eCybersecurity\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eCloud Development\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eSAP Logistics or Finance\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    This is your chance! In our graduate program, you will go through a\r\n    structured six months including trainings, mentoring and jumping into the\r\n    real client projects. You will start your journey at the same time with\r\n    other graduates and together you form your first professional network\r\n    across the company, and your young professionals team is a great source of\r\n    friends too. You will be working with and mentored by the best\r\n    professionals in the field and you are given real business life challenges\r\n    from the very beginning. From day one you will be working in a specific\r\n    team with experienced colleagues while you also have your graduate team as\r\n    a safety net aside.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    WHAT DO WE OFFER:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003ePermanent employment contract\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eCool colleagues and friendly working environment\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eStrong start for a technology-oriented career\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eA tight network of talented individuals with whom to share your first\r\n    steps in IT world\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eInteresting development opportunities with mapped out career paths\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eCompetitive compensation package\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eGood work-life balance\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    DO YOU HAVE WHAT IT TAKES?\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We are looking for a team of extraordinary individuals. You have recently\r\n    graduated or are studying your final year of Master’s degree, Bachelor’s\r\n    degree or similar in Technology or Business. You have studied for example\r\n    computer science and engineering, information networks, information and\r\n    computer science or industrial engineering and, artificial intelligence,\r\n    cloud, data analytics or system thinking might be close to your heart. We\r\n    welcome different fields of study as long as you are passionate about\r\n    technology and digitalization. Show us your passion!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    If you recognize yourself from below, you might be just what we are looking\r\n    for:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n \u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eYou might take pride in being called a (future) tech geek – or at least\r\n    you are not afraid of working closely with them!\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cli\u003eYou want to show your skills in client interactions (we all at Capgemini\r\n    are consultants, after all!)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eYou are eager to learn and you learn quickly. You are ready to work hard\r\n    for your success.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003cli\u003eYou don’t crack under pressure in global and fast-paced working\r\n    environment\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\r\n    \u003cli\u003eAnd of course, you are fluent in both Finnish and English\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Based on your interests and study background we will find the right\r\n    position for you. You will join a dynamic network of experts in our\r\n    collaborative working culture. You will be part of a global company of 200\r\n    000 amazing people but will have freedom and responsibility on your own\r\n    working area.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    ACE YOUR CAREER AND APPLY NOW!\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Please apply by following the link below no later than 30th of September\r\n    2018. Attach your cover letter, CV, certificate of matriculation, your\r\n    study transcript and possible degree diploma, and potential work\r\n    certificates to your application. We will have a fun selection workshop\r\n    taking place on Thursday 4th of October 2018 in Espoo where we invite the\r\n    selected candidates. Please make sure you are prepared to attend to the\r\n    workshop with a short notice.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We hope that you can start your Capgemini career on 29th of October 2018\r\n    but if this does not suit you, we can also discuss other alternatives.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    For more information contact Emma Koskinen, +358 50 3609013. With any\r\n    questions regarding filling in the application, please write to\r\n    recruitmentcapfi.fi@capgemini.com\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    LEARN MORE Learn more about the Capgemini Young Professionals Academy:\r\n    www.capgeminiypa.fi Follow us and the recruitment process:\r\n    www.facebook.com/CapgeminiFinlandCareers\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Instagram: Capgemini.fi\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Love your career. Ace your career.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
