    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Alexandria is launching a new crowdfunding software this fall and is now\r\n    looking for a Software Developer to join their team! This crowdfunding\r\n    software connects investors and Finnish SME companies that need credit and\r\n    is thus helping the Finnish economy by creating opportunities of growth and\r\n    investment for companies. The software has been developed by an outside\r\n    partner and it’s now ready to be handed over for Alexandria. It has been\r\ndeveloped with the following stack:    \u003cstrong\u003eReact, Node.js., Scala, Docker \u003c/strong\u003eand\u003cstrong\u003e AWS\u003c/strong\u003e.\r\n    You don’t have to have experience in all of these technologies yet, but\r\n    willingness to learn and work with them is essential. You can work either\r\n    in Finnish or English depending on your language preferences.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    You can be an experienced developer looking for new challenges or a\r\n    developer in the beginning of your career as the role will be modified to\r\n    match your skills. Depending on your experience the following two options\r\n    are possible:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eMore experienced\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    You have an opportunity to take a Lead Developer role and also be the\r\n    Product Owner for the crowdfunding software. Your main responsibilities in\r\n    the beginning will include product maintenance and further development. As\r\n    a Product Owner you’ll be able to influence which direction the product\r\n    will be developed.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eMore junior\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    If you are in the beginning of your career and don’t want to take the\r\n    ownership of the product yet, it’s also possible to focus only on the\r\n    product maintenance and development tasks. Later on, if you want to take\r\n    more responsibility you have an opportunity to do it. If you don’t have\r\n    previous work experience with programming, we hope that you have done some\r\n    personal programming projects.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    In both cases you will you have a chance to get to know the product first\r\n    and support will be provided by the team if needed. In this position you’ll\r\n    only work with internal stakeholders.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Alexandria and this position can offer you:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Flexibility – at Alexandria people don’t believe in unnecessary\r\n        bureaucracy. You will be given the freedom to work in a way that suits\r\n        you the best, the main thing is to get the job done.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A good atmosphere where employees enjoy socializing and a working\r\n        environment where you can come as you are\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        An opportunity to work with a product that has a concrete impact on the\r\n        Finnish economy and the environment that we live in\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A competitive salary and good employee benefits\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    If you are the Software Developer Alexandria is looking for, send your CV\r\n    and application here:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://apply.atalent.fi/alexandria-software-developer-10-2018"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://apply.atalent.fi/alexandria-software-developer-10-2018\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    by latest on 14.10.2018. Please leave your application documents in\r\n    PDF-format. If you have a GitHub profile or equivalent, we would be happy\r\n    to have a look at it as well.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
