    tags: [],
    description:
      "\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are hiring a Quality Assurance Engineer for fast growing online video\r\n    software company Dream Broker, in the Garage Unit.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Garage is a disruptive technology unit in Dream Broker. It is a small and\r\n    agile team within Dream Broker with motivated and skilled professionals\r\n    creating new apps for global markets. Our focus is on disruptive concepts\r\n    and fast go-to-market operations and iteration. This is a distinctive\r\n    opportunity where you can work in autonomous unit within a well-established\r\n    company.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You feel proud about software that you have passed for release. Your goal\r\n    is to release software products that function well and offer a great\r\n    experience to the users. You want to understand specifications and check\r\n    that every detail works as designed. You are prepared to help us to create\r\n    a video communication product by ensuring world class experience and\r\n    quality.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your role:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e Ensure the quality of the work done by developers and the release\r\n    packages\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eWork alongside the development team, organized in sprints\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eAutomate common and repeatable tasks\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eFurther develop the test environment and QA process\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We value:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eExperience with test automation and continuous integration, as well as\r\n    manual testing\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eFamiliarity with tools like Selenium WebDriver, PhantomJS, JMeter,\r\n    Jenkins, JUnit and XCTest\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eInterest in emerging technologies and related software tools\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eUnderstanding of regression testing, performance testing, security\r\n    testing, REST API testing and feature testing\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eIntermediate-level programming skills (e.g. JavaScript, Java,\r\n    Swift/Objective C, Python)\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003e\r\n    True team player, high sense of responsibility and a ‘getting things\r\n    done’ attitude\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    To be successful in the role you have:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eM.Sc. or B.Sc. degree, preferably in Computer Science, or otherwise\r\n    comparable knowledge and understanding\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eExperience in developing web and mobile applications as part of a team\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eAn attitude and interest for always learning new skills or improving\r\n    current ones\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We offer\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eProfessional team of enthusiastic software professionals creating a new\r\n    way of communication together\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e Good-hearted colleagues, a diverse, international atmosphere and a sea\r\n    view office\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003eAn opportunity for professional growth in a unique work environment\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Your passion towards product craft is contagious, you inspire and motivate\r\n    everyone with exciting product development challenges, celebrate milestones\r\n    and on-schedule shipments.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The job is full-time in Helsinki (Ruoholahti). For further information,\r\n    please contact Talent Acquisition Consultant, Konsta Karppinen (+358 50 470\r\n    5769) or Product Owner, Luyi Ma (+358 442388923). Please send your\r\n    application letter with CV to: tech-careers@dreambroker.fi titled ‘QA\r\n    Engineer’.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Dream Broker is a Finnish online video software company. We revolutionise\r\n    communication in a fun, natural and productive way, with video. Our\r\n    cloud-based software, Dream Broker Studio, enables every employee to easily\r\n    create, edit and share online videos. Dream Broker Studio provides\r\n    customers the highest level of Cyber Security, Information and Data\r\n    Security and GDPR+ level compliance.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Dream Broker was founded in 2007 and has grown to over 100 employees. We\r\n    are one of the fastest growing companies in Europe, with over 800 loyal\r\n    business customers. In addition to our headquarters in Helsinki (Finland),\r\n    we are also located in Turku (Finland), Stockholm (Sweden), Copenhagen\r\n    (Denmark), Oslo (Norway), Amsterdam (the Netherlands) and Berlin (Germany).\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Early on, our goal was to become a significant international player in the\r\n    digital online video software market by 2015. Today, we are the market\r\n    leader in the Nordics, with focus on rapid global expansion via Central and\r\n    Western Europe.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e",
