    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is looking for an exceptional software engineer who has the passion for solving challenging tasks in cutting-edge networking technologies.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Tuxera is the fifth fastest growing software company in Europe, its software is shipped in 3 mobiles, tablets, cars or other devices in every second.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    The candidate will participate in the design and implementation of robust, high-performance, top brand products, has a genuine enthusiasm for results, and\r\n    can achieve them both independently and as a team member.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Responsibilities:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Work on the design, implementation and support of networking protocols and components\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Analyze performance bottlenecks, find and implement improvements\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Debug interoperability and reliability issues, find and implement solutions\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Required Experience:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Expert in C\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Expert in Linux development\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in implementing binary network protocols\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Understanding network configuration in Linux and Windows\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Ability to working in a dynamic, multi-cultural development environment\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Preferred Experience:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        SMB, NFS, DLNA, RTP, RTSP, MPEG-DASH, HLS, or other file streaming and sharing protocols\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiar with security and encryption solutions like OpenSSL, Heimdal, krb5\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Familiar with Linux kernel development, networking layers\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Shell scripting\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Writing portable software, knowledge of several operating systems\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Setting up cloud storage infrastructure with OpenStack Swift\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        BSc or MSc in Computer Science or equivalent skills\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    Benefits:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Dynamic work environment, with flexible working hours.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Laptop, smartphone, health insurance, lunch coupons, and more.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003ch4\u003e\r\n    How to apply:\r\n\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    This position is full-time and located at Tuxera headquarters in Ruoholahti, Helsinki, Finland. The position will be filled once a suitable candidate is\r\n    found. Please apply at the \u003ca target="_blank" href="http://www.tuxera.com/company/careers/job-application/?aguid=21E135C86F884A12AF41987208ED8670"\u003eTuxera website\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
