    description:
      '\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e\r\n        Slush is looking for 2 developers to join salt mine, the legendary\r\n        group of hackers on a mission to help Slush grow beyond its physical\r\n        limitations. We are building software enabling entrepreneurs to access\r\n        who \u0026amp; what they need.\r\n    \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        The legend of the Salt mine started in a tight office room where the\r\n        hackers’ sweat and tears condensed on the thick glass walls to a salty\r\n        substance…\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We are a software product team built of young minds. We are enthusiastic\r\n    about learning and contributing to the greater good. We like to be goofy,\r\n    but when it comes down to software, we take it seriously.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    It’s not about what you are capable of doing right now, but more of what\r\n    you are capable of doing in the future.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eIn short:\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Technologies in use: nodejs, angular, graphql, express server, firebase\r\n    firestore, postgres\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Paid full-time position\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Learning in the core\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Want to jump on a steep learning curve? Now is your chance! ;)\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    SHOOT US A LINE at\r\n    \u003ca href="mailto:rasmus.ekholm@slush.org" target="_blank" tabindex="-1"\u003e\r\n        rasmus.ekholm@slush.org\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Looking forward to hearing back from you,\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    / Rasmus\r\n\u003c/div\u003e',
