      '\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Join Reaktor for the summer 2022\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Hi all!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    It is that time of the year again when sunny summer days feel quite far\r\n    away. However, this is just the time when we’d like you to be dreaming\r\n    about those brighter days, and make sure that you’re making the most out of\r\n    them.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    In the summer 2022, we’re welcoming eager developers to join our Helsinki,\r\n    Tampere and Turku offices and designers to join our Helsinki office. The\r\n    application period runs until Jan 23, 2022. Check out the details and apply\r\n    at\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="http://reaktor.com/junior"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n        id="LPlnk727647"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        reaktor.com/junior\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    !\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
