      '\u003cb\u003eWhat if next summer made all the difference in your future career?\u003cb\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003eFuturice has opened the applications for summer positions for 2020 in\r\nHelsinki and Tampere. We are looking for developers, data scientists and\r\ndesigners. With us, you get to work in real projects and learn from\r\nexperienced professionals.\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eCheck out the opportunities below and apply in one of Finland\'s greatest\r\nnew age digital agencies. Few of our last summer\'s employees shared their\r\nexperience in our blog to give you a better idea on what it\'s like to work\r\nwith us:\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://www.futurice.com/blog/what-is-it-like-to-work-at-futurice-summer-2019"\u003ehttps://www.futurice.com/blog/what-is-it-like-to-work-at-futurice-summer-2019\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003ePositions in Helsinki:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nDeveloper\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-developer-2020-summer-edition-helsinki"\u003ehttps://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-developer-2020-summer-edition-helsinki\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nData Scientist\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-data-scientist-2020-summer-edition-helsinki"\u003ehttps://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-data-scientist-2020-summer-edition-helsinki\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nDesigner\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-designer-2020-summer-edition-helsinki"\u003ehttps://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-designer-2020-summer-edition-helsinki\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003ePositions in Tampere:\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nDeveloper\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-developer-2020-summer-edition-tampere"\u003ehttps://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-developer-2020-summer-edition-tampere\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nData Engineer\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-data-oriented-developer-or-data-engineer-2020-summer-edition-tampere"\u003ehttps://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-data-oriented-developer-or-data-engineer-2020-summer-edition-tampere\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\r\nDesigner\u003cbr\u003e\r\n\u003ca href="https://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-designer-2020-summer-edition-tampere"\u003ehttps://www.futurice.com/careers/futurice-designer-2020-summer-edition-tampere\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eThe applications are open until January 6th (Helsinki) or January 31st\r\n(Tampere) but applications are processed as they come so don\'t wait until\r\nthe last minute.\u003c/p\u003e',
