    description:
      "\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Screenful is a data analytics \u0026amp; visualization startup based in\r\n    Helsinki. We build the future of business intelligence by integrating the\r\n    most commonly used task management tools (such as Jira, Trello, Asana, or\r\n    GitHub), and creating visual dashboards and automated reports that can\r\n    easily be shared with others. Screenful’s cutting edge analytics tools and\r\n    visual dashboards are currently used by 500+ of customers in 40+ countries.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Screenful is looking for a Backend Developer to join the software\r\n    development team located in Helsinki. In this role you will mainly focus on\r\n    the backend of our own Business Intelligence web app along with our CTO and\r\n    the rest of the team. More specifically you will be working on long-term\r\n    product development by participating in different stages of planning,\r\n    coding and testing new features, maintaining existing ones and developing\r\n    our database architecture. The technologies we mainly use are Vue.js,\r\n    Node.js, and PostgreSQL.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    To succeed in this role you should already have some experience in backend\r\n    development for example with Node.js, Go, Java or some other technology.\r\n    You are familiar with SQL and know the basics around relational databases.\r\n    We also value experience in data based software development, data\r\n    warehousing and data processing frameworks. However we don’t expect you to\r\n    tick every box and be an allround expert as the position and tasks can be\r\n    adapted according to your strengths and experience level. More than\r\n    anything we are looking for the “If I don’t know, I’ll figure it out”-type\r\n    of person who is constantly eager to learn more.\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    What we are looking for:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Experience in backend development using Node.js, Java, Go or some other\r\n    technology\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Knowhow with SQL and working with databases\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Solution oriented approach and eagerness to learn more\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Fluency in English\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    We also value experience in:\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Data warehousing and building data processing pipelines\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    - Experience in DevOps and cloud environments such as AWS and Heroku\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    Read more and apply 18.11. the latest:\r\n    https://atalent.fi/open-position/backend-developer-10?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026amp;utm_medium=email?utm_campaign=studo\r\n\u003c/div\u003e",
