    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003eWe are a fintech company that offers tailored investment management software solutions for asset managers, private banks and family offices. We are a growing international company and the leading provider of the industry in Northern Europe. We have a wide expertise in the financial and technology sector, and we constantly develop our software to ensure to always offer the best solution in the market. At the moment, our team consists of 60 employees and due to our growth, we are constantly looking for new experts to join our crew.\u003c/i\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eFA Solutions is looking for a Software Developer to join their team in Helsinki. You will be responsible for developing our software called \u003ca href="https://fasolutions.com/features/"\u003e“FA Platform”\u003c/a\u003e which is used by clients working in Asset Management and investment business areas.\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eYou will be part of our product development team, which consists of other software developers, testers, UX Designer and Technical Writer. Responsibilities in the team are divided flexibly depending on individual skills and interests so you can influence your job description by for example focusing more on front end or back end development. We are working on the whole product development cycle by ourselves from requirement defining to Quality Assurance to make sure the product and it’s modules and applications as a whole flows into production flawlessly.  We develop our product by using Java and other technologies in our stack include HTML, Javascript, React, CSS, Vaadin, Spring Boot, Kubernetes and Microservices. Our software development process is based on agile methodologies - we call it "Scrumban".\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eYou can be a recently graduated developer who has gained experience through studies and own projects or you might already have some work experience in the field. We are seeking for someone who has an interest to work on full stack development and a desire to learn about new technologies. We don’t expect you to know all of the technologies in our stack beforehand, but having experience in at least some of them will help you to succeed. Most importantly, we appreciate a problem solving oriented, systematic and a self driven mindset. \r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eIf you are still finishing your studies, we can also discuss the option to work part-time (minimum 3 days a week) in the beginning of the contract.\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWe require you to:\u003c/b\u003e \r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eHave practical experience in programming (from summer jobs, internships or personal/school projects)\r\n\u003cli\u003eGood skills in one of the following languages: Java, Scala or React  (or some other JavaScript framework)\r\n\u003cli\u003eSystematic way of working and self driven mindset\r\n\u003cli\u003eFluent English skills\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eWe consider as an asset:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eRelevant studies (e.g. software development, computer science, information technology) \r\n\u003cli\u003eExperience of other technologies from our stack (e.g. Spring Boot, Kubernetes, Microservices)\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003eSkill tags:\u003c/b\u003e Java, Scala or React  (or some other JavaScript framework)\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eLue lisää ja hae viimeistään 7.2.: \u003ca href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/software-developer-37?utm_source=tkoaly\u0026utm_medium=email?utm_campaign=studo"\u003ehttps://atalent.fi/open-position/software-developer-37\u003c/a\u003e',
