    tags: [],
    description:
      '\u003ch1\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eSummer Trainee: Opportunity for\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n    \u003cstrong\u003eStudents, Summer 2022\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003c/h1\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Join our friendly community and team up with our top specialists to learn\r\n    about us and our ways of working. You’ll learn from our talented\r\n    specialists, and get to work alongside our teams and leaders – diving deep\r\n    into Solita’s culture. You get to witness how we create impact that lasts\r\n    for our clients and society. By working together with future talent, we\r\n    expand our impact and receive fresh perspectives.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are looking for undergraduate and graduate students in technology and\r\n    business for summer internship in the following areas:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    - Industrial noise analysis\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    - Machine Vision\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    - Cloud Services\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    - Integrations\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    - Software Development and Testing\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    More info about each position can be found here:\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.solita.fi/positions/summer-trainee-opportunity-for-students-summer-2022-4867443003/"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        https://www.solita.fi/positions/summer-trainee-opportunity-for-students-summer-2022-4867443003/\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Team support and collaboration during your internship at Solita\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    To get the most out of your experience at Solita, you will always have\r\n    members of your own internship team near you, consisting of both seasoned\r\n    mentors and fresher Solitans. When possible, you’ll also be paired up with\r\n    a partner-trainee so that you’ll have someone like-minded to buddy-up with\r\n    when needed.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    With a growth mindset and design thinking, we learn, grow and succeed\r\n    together. We are curious and want to constantly learn. You can always ask\r\n    questions, there’s no such thing as a “dumb question” in our ranks!\r\n    Everything we do at Solita is guided by our core values: Being caring,\r\n    easy-going, courageous and passionate, describes well what it means to be\r\n    part of our community.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    At Solita, we combine a high-level of autonomy with the culture of caring.\r\n    Leadership doesn’t need a formal title but it happens as we lead ourselves\r\n    and the teams around us. You care for others and take ownership for your\r\n    own development just as much as the success of the people around you.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You are a perfect combination of creative, driven and enthusiastic, and\r\n    you’re willing and able to learn fast. You are interested in other people,\r\n    and you feel comfortable communicating openly and directly. You are always\r\n    encouraged to share your learnings with others, and will have a fun\r\n    opportunity to do so at the end of your internship.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Interested?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    If this sounds like a perfect step for your future career, please send us\r\n    your application latest on 15th of January 2022. Please specify in the\r\n    title of your cover letter which area you’re applying to.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We will review the applications after the holiday season. The interviews\r\n    will be held during February. The internships will start flexibly during\r\n    May and will last until August or September depending on your availability.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
