    description:
      '\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    Developer Advocate (Sharetribe)\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        Sharetribe is now looking for a first ever Developer Advocate to\r\n        strengthen their team!\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We’re looking for a new teammate to join us as our first ever Developer\r\n    Advocate. You’re an ideal candidate if you are a developer who is motivated\r\n    to teach and assist other developers to thrive at their work. You also\r\n    enjoy building a community.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    In this role your tasks include providing technical consultation to our\r\n    customers. You will have a big role in the developer support rotation, and\r\n    you’ll also actively think of ways to further improve the developer support\r\n    experience. You will empower developers to get the most out of\r\n    \u003ca\r\n        href="https://www.sharetribe.com/products/flex/"\r\n        target="_blank"\r\n        rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n    \u003e\r\n        Sharetribe Flex\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n    What makes you ideal for this role?\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You have basic knowledge of JavaScript and React and know about\r\n            building web applications. You are motivated to learn new tools and\r\n            languages\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You have good communication skills - you like interacting with\r\n            developers and can assist them with their problems\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You’re a creative and skilled writer and comfortable with producing\r\n            video content\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You have a pragmatic attitude and you’re open to new approaches for\r\n            finding solutions in the face of technical constraints\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            You have some work experience from developing and/or customer\r\n            service or marketing\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            Fluency in English\r\n        \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cdiv\u003e\r\n    \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n        Sharetribe can offer you:\r\n    \u003c/p\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n        \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n                Your work will have a global impact. We have more than 1000\r\n                customers in 70+ countries, on 6 continents. They all rely on\r\n                our software to power their marketplace platforms. These\r\n                platforms are already used by millions of people. And we\'re\r\n                just getting started.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n                You will be in charge (really). Sharetribe is not governed by\r\n                outside shareholders. We\'re a profitable company, owned 100% by\r\n                our current team members. You really get to affect how the\r\n                company is run, and what its strategy should be.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n                Full transparency. Our core belief is that to be able to work\r\n                together efficiently, people need to trust each other fully. We\r\n                believe that maximal transparency encourages maximal trust.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n        \u003cli dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n            \u003cp dir="ltr"\u003e\r\n                Perks that matter. We support you in maintaining a healthy life\r\n                balance and offer you significant freedom to design your ideal\r\n                working conditions, including time and location.\r\n            \u003c/p\u003e\r\n        \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003c/div\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Read more and apply at the latest 30.5:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca\r\n    href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/developer-advocate"\r\n    target="_blank"\r\n    rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n\u003e\r\n    https://atalent.fi/open-position/developer-advocate\r\n\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n',
