    description:
      '\u003cstrong\u003e\r\n    Full Stack Developer (Sharetribe)\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cem\u003e\r\n    Sharetribe is looking for a Full Stack Developer to join their engineering\r\n    team!\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We’re looking for a new software expert to join our engineering team to\r\n    build Sharetribe Flex.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca\r\n    href="https://www.sharetribe.com/products/flex/"\r\n    target="_blank"\r\n    rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n\u003e\r\n    Sharetribe Flex\r\n\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    is a headless, API-first Software-as-a-Service solution with a vision to\r\n    make it as easy as possible for software developers to build original,\r\n    established marketplaces fast.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We hope you to:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Have experience in Clojure, ClojureScript and JavaScript and/or in\r\n        DevOps practices and tools\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Have a few years of relevant experience\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Have willingness to learn and encourage us to improve\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Have fluency in English\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Be prepared to join our support and on-call rotations. Our engineering\r\n        team participates in providing high-quality support to our customers.\r\n        You will also have the possibility to join our on-call rotation and\r\n        make sure our operations run smoothly. This possibility is compensated\r\n        fairly.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Be able to work from our Helsinki offices once or twice per week, on\r\n        average. We currently operate in fully remote mode, but in normal\r\n        circumstances our engineering culture is built around having some\r\n        facetime: this is how we feel the happiest and most productive.\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Sharetribe can offer you:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Your work will have a global impact. We have more than 1000 customers\r\n        in 70+ countries, on 6 continents. They all rely on our software to\r\n        power their marketplace platforms. These platforms are already used by\r\n        millions of people. And we’re just getting started.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You will be in charge (really). Sharetribe is not governed by outside\r\n        shareholders. We’re a profitable company, owned 100% by our current\r\n        team members. You really get to affect how the company is run, and what\r\n        its strategy should be.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Full transparency. Our core belief is that to be able to work together\r\n        efficiently, people need to trust each other fully. We believe that\r\n        maximal transparency encourages maximal trust.\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Perks that matter. We support you in maintaining a healthy life balance\r\n        and offer you significant freedom to design your ideal working\r\n        conditions, including time and location.\r\n        \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Read more and apply at the latest 30.5:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca\r\n    href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/full-stack-developer-19"\r\n    target="_blank"\r\n    rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n\u003e\r\n    https://atalent.fi/open-position/full-stack-developer-19\r\n\u003c/a\u003e\r\n',
