    description:
      '\u003cstrong\u003eDevOps Trainee (Supercell) \u003c/strong\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Supercell is looking for a DevOps Trainee to join their team in Helsinki to\r\n    migrate parts of their current monitoring infrastructure to the new\r\n    technology stack. In this position, you will be responsible for\r\n    implementing migration tools that will convert existing dashboards to a new\r\n    platform. The job will require knowledge of Linux operating systems, shell\r\n    scripting and package management. Previous programming experience can be\r\n    beneficial. However, you don’t have to be an experienced DevOps guru right\r\n    away – your drive and motivation to learn will take you far!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We require:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Relevant educational background (e.g. computer science or similar)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Proactive attitude and good problem solving skills\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of Linux operating systems, shell scripting and package\r\n        management\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Proficiency in English, both oral and written\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Knowledge of and interest in the following is seen as an advantage:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Monitoring of server environments\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Skills in Prometheus \u0026amp; Grafana\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Experience in Java, JRuby and/or Python\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Interest in AWS cloud platform\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Knowledge of Munin\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Basic understanding of operating system and database metrics and\r\n        logging\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        A genuine interest in games (experience of Supercell’s games is a big\r\n        plus!)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Why you will love it at Supercell:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        The opportunity to work with an amazing, service-minded, skilled team\r\n        and have fun at work\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Easy-going, enthusiastic, open, and at the same time a very\r\n        results-driven culture\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        An opportunity to follow closely the game industry and development of\r\n        next-generation mobile games\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Versatile job and supportive professional colleagues who boost your\r\n        development\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Great office facilities (including usage of an office gym, with guided\r\n        exercising classes as soon as the circumstances allow this) and\r\n        location in Helsinki\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Flexibility considering working hours and times if needed\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Read more and apply at the latest 23.5.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ca\r\n    href="https://atalent.fi/open-position/devops-trainee"\r\n    target="_blank"\r\n    rel="noopener noreferrer"\r\n\u003e\r\n    https://atalent.fi/open-position/devops-trainee\r\n\u003c/a\u003e\r\n',
