    description:
      '\u003cp\u003e\r\n    \u003cem\u003e\r\n        Helsinki, Finland\r\n        \u003ca href="https://www.10monkeysdigital.com/" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n            www.10monkeysdigital.com\r\n        \u003c/a\u003e\r\n    \u003c/em\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Hello code ninja, nice to see you here!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are a Finnish company, 10Monkeys, specializing in the development of\r\n    digital education and welfare solutions. Our mission is to create a more\r\n    functional society and companies through digital learning. Close at heart\r\n    to us are digital services targeted to children and youth.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We build content-based digital products, from the development of the idea\r\n    to its implementation, to meet the needs of our customers. We are strongly\r\n    involved in the production of content across all projects. In addition to\r\ncustomer projects, we also develop math learning games (    \u003ca href="https://www.10monkeys.com/" target="_blank"\u003ewww.10monkeys.com\u003c/a\u003e\r\n    ), which are played by more than 300 000 students both in Finland and\r\n    internationally. Our team consists of software developers, graphic\r\n    designers and content producers. Our office is located in a funky\r\n    co-working space in Vallila, Helsinki.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Check out our latest projects here:\r\n    \u003ca href="https://www.10monkeysdigital.com/" target="_blank"\u003e\r\n        www.10monkeysdigital.com\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Who are we looking for?\r\n    \u003cbr/\u003e\r\n    We are now looking for a new co-worker, passionate part-time or full-time\r\n    developer with 2+ years\' informal or formal experience in frontend and\r\n    backend web development.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    In addition to good skills in full stack technologies, we will appreciate\r\n    candidates offering the following:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Good written and spoken skills in English\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Eye for detail and love of a smooth user experience\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Here is what we can offer.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Projects with a purpose – the chance to be involved in developing games\r\n        and software used by thousands of users\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Flat organization and superb co-workers\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Flexible working hours\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Part-time or full-time position\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Competitive salary\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Modern office in Helsinki\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Got your attention? Apply today and join us to impact through digital\r\n    learning!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Send your application and CV to work@10monkeys.com\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Please include your salary expectation and if you are interested in a\r\n    part-time or full-time position.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
