    description:
      '\u003ch1\u003e\r\n    Full Stack Web Developer\r\n\u003c/h1\u003e\r\n\u003ch2\u003e\r\n    Who we are\r\n\u003c/h2\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Are you interested in working in a dynamic entrepreneurial environment? If\r\n    you crave for independence and fun projects, join The Extravagant Company\r\n    to work with digital experiments and products focused on fast global\r\n    growth. We are a Finnish company with an international mindset: for us\r\n    English is a must, Finnish is not a requirement.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nCurrently we are working on our main product    \u003ca href="http://www.exolyt.com/" target="_blank"\u003eExolyt\u003c/a\u003e. It started as\r\n    a single experiment and grew into a service that has over one million\r\n    monthly visitors. We offer paid analytical services to TikTok users all\r\n    over the world, helping them to get a better understanding of their\r\n    profiles and the content they post there.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nAnother ongoing experiment of ours is called    \u003ca href="https://thalia.gg/" target="_blank"\u003eThalia\u003c/a\u003e. It is an automated\r\n    news channel based on CS:GO game results. We have more experimental ideas\r\n    in the pool, which we might release later on.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch2\u003e\r\n    Who we are looking for\r\n\u003c/h2\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We are now looking for a Full Stack Web Developer to help us with the\r\n    increasing amount of technical requirements. You will be working in a team\r\n    with our two Full Stack Developers.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    For us “Full Stack Developer” means a person who is a self-starter and can\r\n    work independently with all kinds of complex challenges. You should have\r\n    real world experience from all sides of web development (frontend, backend,\r\n    DevOps, etc.) at least some amount. We welcome you to join us also if your\r\n    original professional background is elsewhere than web development.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch2\u003e\r\n    Expected experience\r\n\u003c/h2\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You would be mainly working with our Exolyt product, developing new\r\n    features in close collaboration with our pilot customers.\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    You should be somewhat familiar with our used technologies:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Javascript as the coding language\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Eslint for code rules\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        NextJS frontend + Vercel hosting\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Node.js backend\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        AWS hosting\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Postgres\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        MongoDB\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        REST APIs\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We also value (but do not require) experience in:\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Data analytics \u0026amp; statistics\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Working with big data amounts and/or data pipelines\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Graphic design\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        UI / UX design (Sketch, Figma, Adobe XD, etc.)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        User interviews\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Customer support\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Business development\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    Requirements are not set in stone. If you are not sure if you have\r\n    everything we need, send us an application and let’s discuss!\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003ch2\u003e\r\n    What we offer\r\n\u003c/h2\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        You can work at anywhere, at any time, with your chosen working\r\n        equipment, as long as you put in the effort towards the agreed goals\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Entrepreneurial environment: no one will micromanage you, but you get\r\n        as much support as you need\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Office at Sörnäinen Helsinki, near the metro (tho it is practically\r\n        empty nowadays)\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003cli\u003e\r\n        Salary according to the level of seniority\r\n    \u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\nIf you have any questions about the position, feel free to contact Jonne at    \u003ca href="mailto:jonne@extravagant.limited"\u003ejonne@extravagant.limited\u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e\r\n\u003cp\u003e\r\n    We will fulfill the position when the right candidate has been found. We\r\n    hope to read your CV + motivation letter soon! Send them to\r\n    \u003ca href="mailto:recruitment@extravagant.limited"\u003e\r\n        recruitment@extravagant.limited\r\n    \u003c/a\u003e\r\n\u003c/p\u003e',
