    description:
      '\u003cp\u003eCombient Foundry launched in 2018, with KONE and Stora Enso, to speed up industrial-grade innovation by working with startups in a way that creates real value for all parties. We are now looking for the brightest, entrepreneurial-minded students to join our exciting journey as Venture Client interns in Automation and Data Analyst - tasks. You will be responsible for designing and executing startup market analysis, analyzing startup deal flow, synthesizing startup scouting results, and participating in internal business development initiatives.\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eWe continuously process data on thousands of startups and scaleups, and create ways to find the diamonds in the rough. You will learn process architecture and automation of startups inflow, evaluations, and communication. According to your interest, you can either be involved in developing one part of the process or build your own idea from scratch. You have competencies and interests in e.g. the best practices regarding UX and automated testing, HTML5, (S)CCS, React, Python + Django, Typescript, RESTFUL services, API design and documentation, SQL or NoSQL databases.\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eThis internship begins in January 2022 and lasts until May 2022. This can be a full-time or part-time (minimum of 60%) internship with flexibility in terms of working hours. In adherence to present recommendations with social distancing, most of the work can be done remotely. Our Helsinki office is located at Bulevardi 44, next to Sinebrychoff Park.\r\n\r\n\u003cp\u003eJa tässä linkki hakuun: \u003ca href="https://combient-foundry.breezy.hr/p/89defd2e774c01-combient-foundry-venture-client-intern"\u003ehttps://combient-foundry.breezy.hr/p/89defd2e774c01-combient-foundry-venture-client-intern\u003c/a\u003e',
